385 public static Level Generate(LevelData levelData, bool mirror, SubmarineInfo startOutpost = null, SubmarineInfo endOutpost = null)
386 {
387 Debug.Assert(levelData.Biome != null);
388 if (levelData.Biome == null) { throw new ArgumentException("Biome was null"); }
389 if (levelData.Size.X <= 0) { throw new ArgumentException("Level width needs to be larger than zero."); }
390 if (levelData.Size.Y <= 0) { throw new ArgumentException("Level height needs to be larger than zero."); }
391
392 Level level = new Level(levelData)
393 {
394 preSelectedStartOutpost = startOutpost,
395 preSelectedEndOutpost = endOutpost
396 };
397 level.Generate(mirror);
398 return level;
399 }
400
401 private void Generate(bool mirror)
402 {
403 Loaded?.Remove();
404 Loaded = this;
405 Generating = true;
406
407 EqualityCheckValues.Clear();
408 EntitiesBeforeGenerate = GetEntities().ToList();
409 EntityCountBeforeGenerate = EntitiesBeforeGenerate.Count();
410
411 if (LevelData.ForceOutpostGenerationParams == null)
412 {
413 StartLocation = GameMain.GameSession?.StartLocation;
414 EndLocation = GameMain.GameSession?.EndLocation;
415 }
416
417 EqualityCheckValues.Add(Rand.Int(int.MaxValue, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient));
418
419 LevelObjectManager = new LevelObjectManager();
420
421 if (Type == LevelData.LevelType.Outpost) { mirror = false; }
422 Mirrored = mirror;
423
424#if CLIENT
425 if (backgroundCreatureManager == null)
426 {
427 var files = ContentPackageManager.EnabledPackages.All.SelectMany(p => p.GetFiles<BackgroundCreaturePrefabsFile>()).ToArray();
428 backgroundCreatureManager = files.Any() ? new BackgroundCreatureManager(files) : new BackgroundCreatureManager("Content/BackgroundCreatures/BackgroundCreaturePrefabs.xml");
429 }
430#endif
431 Stopwatch sw = new Stopwatch();
432 sw.Start();
433
434 PositionsOfInterest = new List<InterestingPosition>();
435 ExtraWalls = new List<LevelWall>();
436 UnsyncedExtraWalls = new List<LevelWall>();
437 bodies = new List<Body>();
438 List<Vector2> sites = new List<Vector2>();
439
440 Voronoi voronoi = new Voronoi(1.0);
441 Rand.SetSyncedSeed(ToolBox.StringToInt(Seed));
442
443#if CLIENT
444 renderer = new LevelRenderer(this);
445#endif
446
447 SeaFloorTopPos = GenerationParams.SeaFloorDepth + GenerationParams.MountainHeightMax + GenerationParams.SeaFloorVariance;
448
449 int minMainPathWidth = Math.Min(GenerationParams.MinTunnelRadius, MaxSubmarineWidth);
450 int minWidth = 500;
451 if (Submarine.MainSub != null)
452 {
453 Rectangle dockedSubBorders = Submarine.MainSub.GetDockedBorders();
454 dockedSubBorders.Inflate(dockedSubBorders.Size.ToVector2() * 0.15f);
455 minWidth = Math.Max(dockedSubBorders.Width, dockedSubBorders.Height);
456 minMainPathWidth = Math.Max(minMainPathWidth, minWidth);
457 minMainPathWidth = Math.Min(minMainPathWidth, MaxSubmarineWidth);
458 }
459 minMainPathWidth = Math.Min(minMainPathWidth, borders.Width / 5);
460 LevelData.MinMainPathWidth = minMainPathWidth;
461
462 Rectangle pathBorders = borders;
463 pathBorders.Inflate(
464 -Math.Min(Math.Min(minMainPathWidth * 2, MaxSubmarineWidth), borders.Width / 5),
465 -Math.Min(minMainPathWidth, borders.Height / 5));
466
467 if (pathBorders.Width <= 0) { throw new InvalidOperationException($"The width of the level's path area is invalid ({pathBorders.Width})"); }
468 if (pathBorders.Height <= 0) { throw new InvalidOperationException($"The height of the level's path area is invalid ({pathBorders.Height})"); }
469
470 startPosition = new Point(
471 (int)MathHelper.Lerp(minMainPathWidth, borders.Width - minMainPathWidth, GenerationParams.StartPosition.X),
472 (int)MathHelper.Lerp(borders.Bottom - Math.Max(minMainPathWidth, ExitDistance * 1.5f), borders.Y + minMainPathWidth, GenerationParams.StartPosition.Y));
473 startExitPosition = new Point(startPosition.X, borders.Bottom);
474
475 endPosition = new Point(
476 (int)MathHelper.Lerp(minMainPathWidth, borders.Width - minMainPathWidth, GenerationParams.EndPosition.X),
477 (int)MathHelper.Lerp(borders.Bottom - Math.Max(minMainPathWidth, ExitDistance * 1.5f), borders.Y + minMainPathWidth, GenerationParams.EndPosition.Y));
478 endExitPosition = new Point(endPosition.X, borders.Bottom);
479
480 EqualityCheckValues.Add(Rand.Int(int.MaxValue, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient));
481
482 //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
483 //generate the initial nodes for the main path and smaller tunnels
484 //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
485
486 Tunnel mainPath = new Tunnel(
487 TunnelType.MainPath,
488 GeneratePathNodes(startPosition, endPosition, pathBorders, null, GenerationParams.MainPathVariance),
489 minMainPathWidth, parentTunnel: null);
490 Tunnels.Add(mainPath);
491
492 Tunnel startPath = null, endPath = null, endHole = null;
493 if (GenerationParams.StartPosition.Y < 0.5f && (Mirrored ? !HasEndOutpost() : !HasStartOutpost()))
494 {
495 startPath = new Tunnel(
496 TunnelType.SidePath,
497 new List<Point>() { startExitPosition, startPosition },
498 minWidth / 2, parentTunnel: mainPath);
499 Tunnels.Add(startPath);
500 }
501 else
502 {
503 startExitPosition = startPosition;
504 }
505 if (GenerationParams.EndPosition.Y < 0.5f && (Mirrored ? !HasStartOutpost() : !HasEndOutpost()))
506 {
507 endPath = new Tunnel(
508 TunnelType.SidePath,
509 new List<Point>() { endPosition, endExitPosition },
510 minWidth / 2, parentTunnel: mainPath);
511 Tunnels.Add(endPath);
512 }
513 else
514 {
515 endExitPosition = endPosition;
516 }
517
518 if (GenerationParams.CreateHoleNextToEnd)
519 {
520 if (Mirrored)
521 {
522 endHole = new Tunnel(
523 TunnelType.SidePath,
524 new List<Point>() { startPosition, startExitPosition, new Point(0, Size.Y) },
525 minWidth / 2, parentTunnel: mainPath);
526 }
527 else
528 {
529 endHole = new Tunnel(
530 TunnelType.SidePath,
531 new List<Point>() { endPosition, endExitPosition, Size },
532 minWidth / 2, parentTunnel: mainPath);
533 }
534 Tunnels.Add(endHole);
535 }
536
537 //create a tunnel from the lowest point in the main path to the abyss
538 //to ensure there's a way to the abyss in all levels
539 Tunnel abyssTunnel = null;
540 if (GenerationParams.CreateHoleToAbyss)
541 {
542 Point lowestPoint = mainPath.Nodes.First();
543 foreach (var pathNode in mainPath.Nodes)
544 {
545 if (pathNode.Y < lowestPoint.Y) { lowestPoint = pathNode; }
546 }
547 abyssTunnel = new Tunnel(
548 TunnelType.SidePath,
549 new List<Point>() { lowestPoint, new Point(lowestPoint.X, 0) },
550 minWidth / 2, parentTunnel: mainPath);
551 Tunnels.Add(abyssTunnel);
552 }
553
554 int sideTunnelCount = Rand.Range(GenerationParams.SideTunnelCount.X, GenerationParams.SideTunnelCount.Y + 1, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
555 for (int j = 0; j < sideTunnelCount; j++)
556 {
557 if (mainPath.Nodes.Count < 4) { break; }
558 var validTunnels = Tunnels.FindAll(t => t.Type != TunnelType.Cave && t != startPath && t != endPath && t != endHole && t != abyssTunnel);
559 Tunnel tunnelToBranchOff = validTunnels[Rand.Int(validTunnels.Count, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient)];
560 if (tunnelToBranchOff == null) { tunnelToBranchOff = mainPath; }
561
562 Point branchStart = tunnelToBranchOff.Nodes[Rand.Range(0, tunnelToBranchOff.Nodes.Count / 3, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient)];
563 Point branchEnd = tunnelToBranchOff.Nodes[Rand.Range(tunnelToBranchOff.Nodes.Count / 3 * 2, tunnelToBranchOff.Nodes.Count - 1, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient)];
564
565 var sidePathNodes = GeneratePathNodes(branchStart, branchEnd, pathBorders, tunnelToBranchOff, GenerationParams.SideTunnelVariance);
566 //make sure the path is wide enough to pass through
567 int pathWidth = Rand.Range(GenerationParams.MinSideTunnelRadius.X, GenerationParams.MinSideTunnelRadius.Y, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
568 Tunnels.Add(new Tunnel(TunnelType.SidePath, sidePathNodes, pathWidth, parentTunnel: tunnelToBranchOff));
569 }
570
571 CalculateTunnelDistanceField(null);
572 GenerateSeaFloorPositions();
573 GenerateAbyssArea();
574 GenerateCaves(mainPath);
575
576 EqualityCheckValues.Add(Rand.Int(int.MaxValue, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient));
577
578 //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
579 //generate voronoi sites
580 //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
581
582 Point siteInterval = GenerationParams.VoronoiSiteInterval;
583 int siteIntervalSqr = (siteInterval.X * siteInterval.X + siteInterval.Y * siteInterval.Y);
584 Point siteVariance = GenerationParams.VoronoiSiteVariance;
585 siteCoordsX = new List<double>((borders.Height / siteInterval.Y) * (borders.Width / siteInterval.Y));
586 siteCoordsY = new List<double>((borders.Height / siteInterval.Y) * (borders.Width / siteInterval.Y));
587 const int caveSiteInterval = 500;
588 for (int x = siteInterval.X / 2; x < borders.Width - siteInterval.X / 2; x += siteInterval.X)
589 {
590 for (int y = siteInterval.Y / 2; y < borders.Height - siteInterval.Y / 2; y += siteInterval.Y)
591 {
592 int siteX = x + Rand.Range(-siteVariance.X, siteVariance.X + 1, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
593 int siteY = y + Rand.Range(-siteVariance.Y, siteVariance.Y + 1, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
594
595 bool closeToTunnel = false;
596 bool closeToCave = false;
597 foreach (Tunnel tunnel in Tunnels)
598 {
599 float minDist = Math.Max(tunnel.MinWidth * 2.0f, Math.Max(siteInterval.X, siteInterval.Y));
600 for (int i = 1; i < tunnel.Nodes.Count; i++)
601 {
602 if (siteX < Math.Min(tunnel.Nodes[i - 1].X, tunnel.Nodes[i].X) - minDist) { continue; }
603 if (siteX > Math.Max(tunnel.Nodes[i - 1].X, tunnel.Nodes[i].X) + minDist) { continue; }
604 if (siteY < Math.Min(tunnel.Nodes[i - 1].Y, tunnel.Nodes[i].Y) - minDist) { continue; }
605 if (siteY > Math.Max(tunnel.Nodes[i - 1].Y, tunnel.Nodes[i].Y) + minDist) { continue; }
606
607 double tunnelDistSqr = MathUtils.LineSegmentToPointDistanceSquared(tunnel.Nodes[i - 1], tunnel.Nodes[i], new Point(siteX, siteY));
608 if (Math.Sqrt(tunnelDistSqr) < minDist)
609 {
610 closeToTunnel = true;
611 //tunnelDistSqr = MathUtils.LineSegmentToPointDistanceSquared(tunnel.Nodes[i - 1], tunnel.Nodes[i], new Point(siteX, siteY));
612 if (tunnel.Type == TunnelType.Cave)
613 {
614 closeToCave = true;
615 }
616 break;
617 }
618 }
619 }
620
621 if (!closeToTunnel)
622 {
623 //make the graph less dense (90% less nodes) in areas far away from tunnels where we don't need a lot of geometry
624 if (Rand.Range(0, 10, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient) != 0) { continue; }
625 }
626
627 if (!TooClose(siteX, siteY))
628 {
629 siteCoordsX.Add(siteX);
630 siteCoordsY.Add(siteY);
631 }
632
633 if (closeToCave)
634 {
635 for (int x2 = x; x2 < x + siteInterval.X; x2 += caveSiteInterval)
636 {
637 for (int y2 = y; y2 < y + siteInterval.Y; y2 += caveSiteInterval)
638 {
639 int caveSiteX = x2 + Rand.Int(caveSiteInterval / 2, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
640 int caveSiteY = y2 + Rand.Int(caveSiteInterval / 2, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
641
642 if (!TooClose(caveSiteX, caveSiteY))
643 {
644 siteCoordsX.Add(caveSiteX);
645 siteCoordsY.Add(caveSiteY);
646 }
647 }
648 }
649 }
650 }
651 }
652
653 bool TooClose(double siteX, double siteY)
654 {
655 for (int i = 0; i < siteCoordsX.Count; i++)
656 {
657 if (MathUtils.DistanceSquared(siteCoordsX[i], siteCoordsY[i], siteX, siteY) < 10.0f * 10.0f)
658 {
659 return true;
660 }
661 }
662 return false;
663 }
664
665 for (int i = 0; i < siteCoordsX.Count; i++)
666 {
667 Debug.Assert(
668 siteCoordsX[i] > 0 || siteCoordsY[i] > 0,
669 $"Potential error in level generation: a voronoi site was outside the bounds of the level ({siteCoordsX[i]}, {siteCoordsY[i]})");
670 Debug.Assert(
671 siteCoordsX[i] < borders.Width || siteCoordsY[i] < borders.Height,
672 $"Potential error in level generation: a voronoi site was outside the bounds of the level ({siteCoordsX[i]}, {siteCoordsY[i]})");
673 for (int j = i + 1; j < siteCoordsX.Count; j++)
674 {
675 Debug.Assert(
676 MathUtils.DistanceSquared(siteCoordsX[i], siteCoordsY[i], siteCoordsX[j], siteCoordsY[j]) > 1.0f,
677 "Potential error in level generation: two voronoi sites are extremely close to each other.");
678 }
679 }
680
681 EqualityCheckValues.Add(Rand.Int(int.MaxValue, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient));
682
683 //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
684 // construct the voronoi graph and cells
685 //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
686
687 Stopwatch sw2 = new Stopwatch();
688 sw2.Start();
689
690 Debug.Assert(siteCoordsX.Count == siteCoordsY.Count);
691 List<GraphEdge> graphEdges = voronoi.MakeVoronoiGraph(siteCoordsX.ToArray(), siteCoordsY.ToArray(), borders.Width, borders.Height);
692
693 Debug.WriteLine("MakeVoronoiGraph: " + sw2.ElapsedMilliseconds + " ms");
694 sw2.Restart();
695
696 //construct voronoi cells based on the graph edges
697 cells = CaveGenerator.GraphEdgesToCells(graphEdges, borders, GridCellSize, out cellGrid);
698
699 GenerateAbyssGeometry();
700 GenerateAbyssPositions();
701
702 Debug.WriteLine("find cells: " + sw2.ElapsedMilliseconds + " ms");
703 sw2.Restart();
704
705 //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
706 // generate a path through the tunnel nodes
707 //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
708
709 List<VoronoiCell> pathCells = new List<VoronoiCell>();
710 foreach (Tunnel tunnel in Tunnels)
711 {
712 CaveGenerator.GeneratePath(tunnel, this);
713 if (tunnel.Type == TunnelType.MainPath || tunnel.Type == TunnelType.SidePath)
714 {
715 if (tunnel != startPath && tunnel != endPath && tunnel != endHole)
716 {
717 var distinctCells = tunnel.Cells.Distinct().ToList();
718 for (int i = 2; i < distinctCells.Count; i += 3)
719 {
720 PositionsOfInterest.Add(new InterestingPosition(
721 new Point((int)distinctCells[i].Site.Coord.X, (int)distinctCells[i].Site.Coord.Y),
722 tunnel.Type == TunnelType.MainPath ? PositionType.MainPath : PositionType.SidePath,
723 Caves.Find(cave => cave.Tunnels.Contains(tunnel))));
724 }
725 }
726 }
727
728 bool connectToParentTunnel = tunnel.Type != TunnelType.Cave || tunnel.ParentTunnel.Type == TunnelType.Cave;
729 GenerateWaypoints(tunnel, parentTunnel: connectToParentTunnel ? tunnel.ParentTunnel : null);
730
731 EnlargePath(tunnel.Cells, tunnel.MinWidth);
732 foreach (var pathCell in tunnel.Cells)
733 {
734 MarkEdges(pathCell, tunnel.Type);
735 foreach (GraphEdge edge in pathCell.Edges)
736 {
737 var adjacent = edge.AdjacentCell(pathCell);
738 if (adjacent != null)
739 {
740 MarkEdges(adjacent, tunnel.Type);
741 }
742 }
743 if (!pathCells.Contains(pathCell))
744 {
745 pathCells.Add(pathCell);
746 }
747 }
748
749 static void MarkEdges(VoronoiCell cell, TunnelType tunnelType)
750 {
751 foreach (GraphEdge edge in cell.Edges)
752 {
753 switch (tunnelType)
754 {
755 case TunnelType.MainPath:
756 edge.NextToMainPath = true;
757 break;
758 case TunnelType.SidePath:
759 edge.NextToSidePath = true;
760 break;
761 case TunnelType.Cave:
762 edge.NextToCave = true;
763 break;
764 }
765 }
766 }

1311 private List<Point> GeneratePathNodes(Point startPosition, Point endPosition, Rectangle pathBorders, Tunnel parentTunnel, float variance)
1312 {
1313 List<Point> pathNodes = new List<Point> { startPosition };
1314
1315 Point nodeInterval = GenerationParams.MainPathNodeIntervalRange;
1316
1317 for (int x = startPosition.X + nodeInterval.X;
1318 x < endPosition.X - nodeInterval.X;
1319 x += Rand.Range(nodeInterval.X, nodeInterval.Y, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient))
1320 {
1321 Point nodePos = new Point(x, Rand.Range(pathBorders.Y, pathBorders.Bottom, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient));
1322
1323 //allow placing the 2nd main path node at any height regardless of variance
1324 //(otherwise low variance will always make the main path go through the upper part of the level)
1325 if (pathNodes.Count > 2 || parentTunnel != null)
1326 {
1327 nodePos.Y = (int)MathHelper.Clamp(
1328 nodePos.Y,
1329 pathNodes.Last().Y - pathBorders.Height * variance * 0.5f,
1330 pathNodes.Last().Y + pathBorders.Height * variance * 0.5f);
1331 }
1332 if (pathNodes.Count == 1)
1333 {
1334 //if the path starts below the center of the level, head up and vice versa
1335 //to utilize as much of the vertical space as possible
1336 nodePos.Y = (int)(startPosition.Y + Math.Abs(nodePos.Y - startPosition.Y) * -Math.Sign(nodePos.Y - pathBorders.Center.Y));
1337 nodePos.Y = MathHelper.Clamp(nodePos.Y, pathBorders.Y, pathBorders.Bottom);
1338 }
1339
1340 //prevent intersections with other tunnels
1341 foreach (Tunnel tunnel in Tunnels)
1342 {
1343 for (int i = 1; i < tunnel.Nodes.Count; i++)
1344 {
1345 Point node1 = tunnel.Nodes[i - 1];
1346 Point node2 = tunnel.Nodes[i];
1347 if (node1.X >= nodePos.X) { continue; }
1348 if (node2.X <= pathNodes.Last().X) { continue; }
1349 if (MathUtils.NearlyEqual(node1.X, pathNodes.Last().X)) { continue; }
1350 if (Math.Abs(node1.Y - nodePos.Y) > tunnel.MinWidth && Math.Abs(node2.Y - nodePos.Y) > tunnel.MinWidth &&
1351 !MathUtils.LinesIntersect(node1.ToVector2(), node2.ToVector2(), pathNodes.Last().ToVector2(), nodePos.ToVector2()))
1352 {
1353 continue;
1354 }
1355
1356 if (nodePos.Y < pathNodes.Last().Y)
1357 {
1358 nodePos.Y = Math.Min(Math.Max(node1.Y, node2.Y) + tunnel.MinWidth * 2, pathBorders.Bottom);
1359 }
1360 else
1361 {
1362 nodePos.Y = Math.Max(Math.Min(node1.Y, node2.Y) - tunnel.MinWidth * 2, pathBorders.Y);
1363 }
1364 break;
1365 }
1366 }
1367
1368 pathNodes.Add(nodePos);
1369 }
1370
1371 if (pathNodes.Count == 1)
1372 {
1373 pathNodes.Add(new Point(pathBorders.Center.X, pathBorders.Y));
1374 }
1375
1376 pathNodes.Add(endPosition);
1377 return pathNodes;
1378 }
1379
1380 private List<VoronoiCell> CreateHoles(float holeProbability, Rectangle limits, int submarineSize)
1381 {
1382 List<VoronoiCell> toBeRemoved = new List<VoronoiCell>();
1383 foreach (VoronoiCell cell in cells)
1384 {
1385 if (cell.Edges.Any(e => e.NextToCave)) { continue; }
1386 if (Rand.Range(0.0f, 1.0f, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient) > holeProbability) { continue; }
1387 if (!limits.Contains(cell.Site.Coord.X, cell.Site.Coord.Y)) { continue; }
1388
1389 float closestDist = 0.0f;
1390 Point? closestTunnelNode = null;
1391 foreach (Tunnel tunnel in Tunnels)
1392 {
1393 foreach (Point node in tunnel.Nodes)
1394 {
1395 float dist = Math.Abs(cell.Center.X - node.X);
1396 if (closestTunnelNode == null || dist < closestDist)
1397 {
1398 closestDist = dist;
1399 closestTunnelNode = node;
1400 }
1401 }
1402 }
1403
1404 if (closestTunnelNode != null && closestTunnelNode.Value.Y < cell.Center.Y) { continue; }
1405
1406 toBeRemoved.Add(cell);
1407 }
1408
1409 return toBeRemoved;
1410 }
1411
1412 private void EnlargePath(List<VoronoiCell> pathCells, float minWidth)
1413 {
1414 if (minWidth <= 0.0f) { return; }
1415
1416 List<VoronoiCell> removedCells = GetTooCloseCells(pathCells, minWidth);
1417 foreach (VoronoiCell removedCell in removedCells)
1418 {
1419 if (removedCell.CellType == CellType.Path) { continue; }
1420
1421 pathCells.Add(removedCell);
1422 removedCell.CellType = CellType.Path;
1423 }
1424 }

1426 private void GenerateWaypoints(Tunnel tunnel, Tunnel parentTunnel)
1427 {
1428 if (tunnel.Cells.Count == 0) { return; }
1429
1430 List<WayPoint> wayPoints = new List<WayPoint>();
1431 WayPoint prevWayPoint = null;
1432 for (int i = 0; i < tunnel.Cells.Count; i++)
1433 {
1434 tunnel.Cells[i].CellType = CellType.Path;
1435 var newWaypoint = new WayPoint(new Rectangle((int)tunnel.Cells[i].Site.Coord.X, (int)tunnel.Cells[i].Center.Y, 10, 10), null)
1436 {
1437 Tunnel = tunnel
1438 };
1439 wayPoints.Add(newWaypoint);
1440
1441 if (prevWayPoint != null)
1442 {
1443 bool solidCellBetween = false;
1444 foreach (GraphEdge edge in tunnel.Cells[i].Edges)
1445 {
1446 if (edge.AdjacentCell(tunnel.Cells[i])?.CellType == CellType.Solid &&
1447 MathUtils.LinesIntersect(newWaypoint.WorldPosition, prevWayPoint.WorldPosition, edge.Point1, edge.Point2))
1448 {
1449 solidCellBetween = true;
1450 break;
1451 }
1452 }
1453
1454 if (solidCellBetween)
1455 {
1456 //something between the previous waypoint and this one
1457 // -> find the edge that connects the cells and place a waypoint there, instead of connecting the centers of the cells directly
1458 var edgeBetweenCells = tunnel.Cells[i].Edges.Find(e => e.AdjacentCell(tunnel.Cells[i]) == tunnel.Cells[i - 1]);
1459 if (edgeBetweenCells != null)
1460 {
1461 var edgeWaypoint = new WayPoint(new Rectangle((int)edgeBetweenCells.Center.X, (int)edgeBetweenCells.Center.Y, 10, 10), null)
1462 {
1463 Tunnel = tunnel
1464 };
1465 prevWayPoint.ConnectTo(edgeWaypoint);
1466 prevWayPoint = edgeWaypoint;
1467 }
1468 }
1469 prevWayPoint.ConnectTo(newWaypoint);
1470
1471 //look back at the tunnel cells before the previous one, and see if the current cell shares edges with them
1472 //= if we can "skip" from cell #1 to cell #3, create a waypoint between them.
1473 //Fixes there sometimes not being a path past a destructible ice chunk even if there's space to go past it.
1474 for (int j = i - 2; j > 0 && j > i - 5; j--)
1475 {
1476 foreach (GraphEdge edge in tunnel.Cells[i].Edges)
1477 {
1478 if (Vector2.DistanceSquared(edge.Point1, edge.Point2) < 30.0f * 30.0f) { continue; }
1479 if (!edge.IsSolid && edge.AdjacentCell(tunnel.Cells[i]) == tunnel.Cells[j])
1480 {
1481 var edgeWaypoint = new WayPoint(new Rectangle((int)edge.Center.X, (int)edge.Center.Y, 10, 10), null)
1482 {
1483 Tunnel = tunnel
1484 };
1485 wayPoints[j].ConnectTo(edgeWaypoint);
1486 edgeWaypoint.ConnectTo(newWaypoint);
1487 break;
1488 }
1489 }
1490 }
1491 }
1492 prevWayPoint = newWaypoint;
1493 }
1494
1495 tunnel.WayPoints.AddRange(wayPoints);
1496
1497 //connect to the tunnel we're branching off from
1498 if (parentTunnel != null)
1499 {
1500 var parentStart = FindClosestWayPoint(wayPoints.First().WorldPosition, parentTunnel);
1501 if (parentStart != null)
1502 {
1503 wayPoints.First().ConnectTo(parentStart);
1504 }
1505 if (tunnel.Type != TunnelType.Cave || tunnel.ParentTunnel.Type == TunnelType.Cave)
1506 {
1507 var parentEnd = FindClosestWayPoint(wayPoints.Last().WorldPosition, parentTunnel);
1508 if (parentEnd != null)
1509 {
1510 wayPoints.Last().ConnectTo(parentEnd);
1511 }
1512 }
1513 }
1514 }
1515
1516 private void ConnectWaypoints(Tunnel tunnel, Tunnel parentTunnel)
1517 {
1518 foreach (WayPoint wayPoint in tunnel.WayPoints)
1519 {
1520 var closestWaypoint = FindClosestWayPoint(wayPoint.WorldPosition, parentTunnel);
1521 if (closestWaypoint == null) { continue; }
1522 if (Submarine.PickBody(
1523 ConvertUnits.ToSimUnits(wayPoint.WorldPosition),
1524 ConvertUnits.ToSimUnits(closestWaypoint.WorldPosition), collisionCategory: Physics.CollisionLevel | Physics.CollisionWall) == null)
1525 {
1526 float step = ConvertUnits.ToDisplayUnits(Steering.AutopilotMinDistToPathNode) * 0.8f;
1527 ConnectWaypoints(wayPoint, closestWaypoint, step).ForEach(wp => wp.Tunnel = tunnel);
1528 }
1529 }
1530 }
1531
1532 private List<WayPoint> ConnectWaypoints(WayPoint wp1, WayPoint wp2, float interval)
1533 {
1534 List<WayPoint> newWaypoints = new List<WayPoint>();
1535
1536 Vector2 diff = wp2.WorldPosition - wp1.WorldPosition;
1537 float dist = diff.Length();
1538
1539 WayPoint prevWaypoint = wp1;
1540 for (float x = interval; x < dist - interval; x += interval)
1541 {
1542 var newWaypoint = new WayPoint(wp1.WorldPosition + (diff / dist * x), SpawnType.Path, submarine: null);
1543 prevWaypoint.ConnectTo(newWaypoint);
1544 prevWaypoint = newWaypoint;
1545 newWaypoints.Add(newWaypoint);
1546 }
1547 prevWaypoint.ConnectTo(wp2);
1548
1549 return newWaypoints;
1550 }
1551
1552 private static WayPoint FindClosestWayPoint(Vector2 worldPosition, Tunnel otherTunnel)
1553 {
1554 return FindClosestWayPoint(worldPosition, otherTunnel.WayPoints);
1555 }
1556
1557 private static WayPoint FindClosestWayPoint(Vector2 worldPosition, IEnumerable<WayPoint> waypoints, Func<WayPoint, bool> filter = null)
1558 {
1559 float closestDist = float.PositiveInfinity;
1560 WayPoint closestWayPoint = null;
1561 foreach (WayPoint otherWayPoint in waypoints)
1562 {
1563 float dist = Vector2.DistanceSquared(otherWayPoint.WorldPosition, worldPosition);
1564 if (dist < closestDist)
1565 {
1566 if (filter != null)
1567 {
1568 if (!filter(otherWayPoint)) { continue; }
1569 }
1570 closestDist = dist;
1571 closestWayPoint = otherWayPoint;
1572 }
1573 }
1574 return closestWayPoint;
1575 }

1577 private List<VoronoiCell> GetTooCloseCells(List<VoronoiCell> emptyCells, float minDistance)
1578 {
1579 List<VoronoiCell> tooCloseCells = new List<VoronoiCell>();
1580 if (minDistance <= 0.0f) { return tooCloseCells; }
1581 foreach (var cell in emptyCells.Distinct())
1582 {
1583 foreach (var tooCloseCell in GetTooCloseCells(cell.Center, minDistance))
1584 {
1585 if (!tooCloseCells.Contains(tooCloseCell))
1586 {
1587 tooCloseCells.Add(tooCloseCell);
1588 }
1589 }
1590 }
1591 return tooCloseCells;
1592 }
1593
1594 public List<VoronoiCell> GetTooCloseCells(Vector2 position, float minDistance)
1595 {
1596 HashSet<VoronoiCell> tooCloseCells = new HashSet<VoronoiCell>();
1597 var closeCells = GetCells(position, searchDepth: Math.Max((int)Math.Ceiling(minDistance / GridCellSize), 3));
1598 float minDistSqr = minDistance * minDistance;
1599 foreach (VoronoiCell cell in closeCells)
1600 {
1601 bool tooClose = false;
1602 foreach (GraphEdge edge in cell.Edges)
1603 {
1604 if (Vector2.DistanceSquared(edge.Point1, position) < minDistSqr ||
1605 Vector2.DistanceSquared(edge.Point2, position) < minDistSqr ||
1606 MathUtils.LineSegmentToPointDistanceSquared(edge.Point1.ToPoint(), edge.Point2.ToPoint(), position.ToPoint()) < minDistSqr)
1607 {
1608 tooClose = true;
1609 break;
1610 }
1611 }
1612 if (tooClose) { tooCloseCells.Add(cell); }
1613 }
1614 return tooCloseCells.ToList();
1615 }

1617 private void GenerateAbyssPositions()
1618 {
1619 int count = 10;
1620 for (int i = 0; i < count; i++)
1621 {

1642 private void GenerateAbyssArea()
1643 {
1644 int abyssStartY = borders.Y - 5000;
1645 int abyssEndY = Math.Max(abyssStartY - 100000, BottomPos + 1000);
1646 int abyssHeight = abyssStartY - abyssEndY;
1647
1648 if (abyssHeight < 0)
1649 {
1650 abyssStartY = borders.Y;
1651 abyssEndY = BottomPos;
1652 if (abyssStartY - abyssEndY < 1000)
1653 {
1654#if DEBUG
1655 DebugConsole.ThrowError("Not enough space to generate Abyss in the level. You may want to move the ocean floor deeper.");
1656#else
1657 DebugConsole.AddWarning("Not enough space to generate Abyss in the level. You may want to move the ocean floor deeper.");
1658#endif
1659 }
1660 }
1661 else
1662 {
1663 //if the bottom of the abyss area is below crush depth, try to move it up to keep (most) of the abyss content above crush depth
1664 if (abyssEndY + CrushDepth < 0)
1665 {
1666 abyssEndY += Math.Min(-(abyssEndY + (int)CrushDepth), abyssHeight / 2);
1667 }
1668
1669 if (abyssStartY - abyssEndY < 10000)
1670 {
1671 abyssStartY = borders.Y;
1672 }
1673 }
1674
1675 AbyssArea = new Rectangle(borders.X, abyssEndY, borders.Width, abyssStartY - abyssEndY);
1676 }
1677
1678 private void GenerateAbyssGeometry()
1679 {
1680 //TODO: expose island parameters
1681
1682 Voronoi voronoi = new Voronoi(1.0);
1683 Point siteInterval = new Point(500, 500);
1684 Point siteVariance = new Point(200, 200);
1685
1686 Point islandSize = Vector2.Lerp(
1687 GenerationParams.AbyssIslandSizeMin.ToVector2(),
1688 GenerationParams.AbyssIslandSizeMax.ToVector2(),
1689 Rand.Range(0.0f, 1.0f, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient)).ToPoint();
1690
1691 if (AbyssArea.Height < islandSize.Y) { return; }
1692
1693 int islandCount = GenerationParams.AbyssIslandCount;
1694 for (int i = 0; i < islandCount; i++)
1695 {
1696 Point islandPosition = Point.Zero;
1697 Rectangle islandArea = new Rectangle(islandPosition, islandSize);
1698
1699 //prevent overlaps
1700 int tries = 0;
1701 const int MaxTries = 20;
1702 do
1703 {
1704 islandPosition = new Point(
1705 Rand.Range(AbyssArea.X, AbyssArea.Right - islandSize.X, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient),
1706 Rand.Range(AbyssArea.Y, AbyssArea.Bottom - islandSize.Y, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient));
1707
1708 //move the island above the sea floor geometry
1709 islandPosition.Y = Math.Max(islandPosition.Y, (int)GetBottomPosition(islandPosition.X).Y + 500);
1710 islandPosition.Y = Math.Max(islandPosition.Y, (int)GetBottomPosition(islandPosition.X + islandArea.Width).Y + 500);
1711
1712 islandArea.Location = islandPosition;
1713
1714 tries++;
1715 } while ((AbyssIslands.Any(island => island.Area.Intersects(islandArea)) || islandArea.Bottom > AbyssArea.Bottom) && tries < MaxTries);
1716
1717 if (tries >= MaxTries)
1718 {
1719 break;
1720 }
1721
1722 if (Rand.Range(0.0f, 1.0f, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient) > GenerationParams.AbyssIslandCaveProbability)
1723 {
1724 float radiusVariance = Math.Min(islandArea.Width, islandArea.Height) * 0.1f;
1725 var vertices = CaveGenerator.CreateRandomChunk(islandArea.Width - (int)(radiusVariance * 2), islandArea.Height - (int)(radiusVariance * 2), 16, radiusVariance: radiusVariance);
1726 Vector2 position = islandArea.Center.ToVector2();
1727 for (int j = 0; j < vertices.Count; j++)
1728 {
1729 vertices[j] += position;
1730 }
1731 var newChunk = new LevelWall(vertices, GenerationParams.WallColor, this, createBody: false);
1732 AbyssIslands.Add(new AbyssIsland(islandArea, newChunk.Cells));
1733 continue;
1734 }
1735
1736 var siteCoordsX = new List<double>((islandSize.Y / siteInterval.Y) * (islandSize.X / siteInterval.Y));
1737 var siteCoordsY = new List<double>((islandSize.Y / siteInterval.Y) * (islandSize.X / siteInterval.Y));
1738
1739 for (int x = islandArea.X; x < islandArea.Right; x += siteInterval.X)
1740 {
1741 for (int y = islandArea.Y; y < islandArea.Bottom; y += siteInterval.Y)
1742 {
1743 siteCoordsX.Add(x + Rand.Range(-siteVariance.X, siteVariance.X, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient));
1744 siteCoordsY.Add(y + Rand.Range(-siteVariance.Y, siteVariance.Y, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient));
1745 }
1746 }
1747
1748 var graphEdges = voronoi.MakeVoronoiGraph(siteCoordsX.ToArray(), siteCoordsY.ToArray(), islandArea);
1749 var islandCells = CaveGenerator.GraphEdgesToCells(graphEdges, islandArea, GridCellSize, out var cellGrid);
1750
1751 //make the island elliptical
1752 for (int j = islandCells.Count - 1; j >= 0; j--)
1753 {
1754 var cell = islandCells[j];
1755 double xDiff = (cell.Site.Coord.X - islandArea.Center.X) / (islandArea.Width * 0.5);
1756 double yDiff = (cell.Site.Coord.Y - islandArea.Center.Y) / (islandArea.Height * 0.5);
1757
1758 //a conical stalactite-like shape at the bottom
1759 if (yDiff < 0) { xDiff += xDiff * Math.Abs(yDiff); }
1760
1761 double normalizedDist = Math.Sqrt(xDiff * xDiff + yDiff * yDiff);
1762 if (normalizedDist > 0.95 ||
1763 cell.Edges.Any(e => MathUtils.NearlyEqual(e.Point1.X, islandArea.X)) ||
1764 cell.Edges.Any(e => MathUtils.NearlyEqual(e.Point1.X, islandArea.Right)) ||
1765 cell.Edges.Any(e => MathUtils.NearlyEqual(e.Point1.Y, islandArea.Y)) ||
1766 cell.Edges.Any(e => MathUtils.NearlyEqual(e.Point1.Y, islandArea.Bottom)))
1767 {
1768 islandCells[j].CellType = CellType.Removed;
1769 islandCells.RemoveAt(j);
1770 }
1771 }
1772
1773 var caveParams = CaveGenerationParams.GetRandom(GenerationParams, abyss: true, rand: Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
1774
1775 float caveScaleRelativeToIsland = 0.7f;
1776 GenerateCave(
1777 caveParams, Tunnels.First(),
1778 new Point(islandArea.Center.X, islandArea.Center.Y + (int)(islandArea.Size.Y * (1.0f - caveScaleRelativeToIsland)) / 2),
1779 new Point((int)(islandArea.Size.X * caveScaleRelativeToIsland), (int)(islandArea.Size.Y * caveScaleRelativeToIsland)));
1780 AbyssIslands.Add(new AbyssIsland(islandArea, islandCells));
1781 }
1782 }

1858 private void GenerateCave(CaveGenerationParams caveParams, Tunnel parentTunnel, Point cavePos, Point caveSize)
1859 {
1860 Rectangle caveArea = new Rectangle(cavePos - new Point(caveSize.X / 2, caveSize.Y / 2), caveSize);
1861 Point closestParentNode = parentTunnel.Nodes.First();
1862 double closestDist = double.PositiveInfinity;
1863 foreach (Point node in parentTunnel.Nodes)
1864 {
1865 if (caveArea.Contains(node)) { continue; }
1866 double dist = MathUtils.DistanceSquared((double)node.X, (double)node.Y, (double)cavePos.X, (double)cavePos.Y);
1867 if (dist < closestDist)
1868 {
1869 closestParentNode = node;
1870 closestDist = dist;
1871 }
1872 }
1873
1874 if (!MathUtils.GetLineRectangleIntersection(closestParentNode.ToVector2(), cavePos.ToVector2(), new Rectangle(caveArea.X, caveArea.Y + caveArea.Height, caveArea.Width, caveArea.Height), out Vector2 caveStartPosVector))
1875 {
1876 caveStartPosVector = caveArea.Location.ToVector2();
1877 }
1878
1879 Point caveStartPos = caveStartPosVector.ToPoint();
1880 Point caveEndPos = cavePos - (caveStartPos - cavePos);
1881
1882 Cave cave = new Cave(caveParams, caveArea, caveStartPos, caveEndPos);
1883 Caves.Add(cave);
1884
1885 var caveSegments = MathUtils.GenerateJaggedLine(
1886 caveStartPos.ToVector2(), caveEndPos.ToVector2(),
1887 iterations: 3,
1888 offsetAmount: Vector2.Distance(caveStartPos.ToVector2(), caveEndPos.ToVector2()) * 0.75f,
1889 bounds: caveArea);
1890
1891 if (!caveSegments.Any()) { return; }
1892
1893 List<Tunnel> caveBranches = new List<Tunnel>();
1894
1895 var tunnel = new Tunnel(TunnelType.Cave, SegmentsToNodes(caveSegments), 100, parentTunnel);
1896 Tunnels.Add(tunnel);
1897 caveBranches.Add(tunnel);
1898
1899 int branches = Rand.Range(caveParams.MinBranchCount, caveParams.MaxBranchCount + 1, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
1900 for (int j = 0; j < branches; j++)
1901 {
1902 Tunnel parentBranch = caveBranches.GetRandom(Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
1903 Vector2 branchStartPos = parentBranch.Nodes[Rand.Int(parentBranch.Nodes.Count / 2, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient)].ToVector2();
1904 Vector2 branchEndPos = parentBranch.Nodes[Rand.Range(parentBranch.Nodes.Count / 2, parentBranch.Nodes.Count, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient)].ToVector2();
1905 var branchSegments = MathUtils.GenerateJaggedLine(
1906 branchStartPos, branchEndPos,
1907 iterations: 3,
1908 offsetAmount: Vector2.Distance(branchStartPos, branchEndPos) * 0.75f,
1909 bounds: caveArea);
1910 if (!branchSegments.Any()) { continue; }
1911
1912 var branch = new Tunnel(TunnelType.Cave, SegmentsToNodes(branchSegments), 0, parentBranch);
1913 Tunnels.Add(branch);
1914 caveBranches.Add(branch);
1915 }
1916
1917 foreach (Tunnel branch in caveBranches)
1918 {
1919 var node = branch.Nodes.Last();
1920 PositionsOfInterest.Add(new InterestingPosition(node, node.Y < AbyssArea.Bottom ? PositionType.AbyssCave : PositionType.Cave, cave));
1921 cave.Tunnels.Add(branch);
1922 }
1923
1924 static List<Point> SegmentsToNodes(List<Vector2[]> segments)
1925 {
1926 List<Point> nodes = new List<Point>();
1927 foreach (Vector2[] segment in segments)
1928 {
1929 nodes.Add(segment[0].ToPoint());
1930 }
1931 nodes.Add(segments.Last()[1].ToPoint());
1932 return nodes;
1933 }
1934 }

1936 private void GenerateRuin(Point ruinPos, bool mirror)
1937 {
1938 var ruinGenerationParams = RuinGenerationParams.RuinParams.GetRandom(Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
1939
1940 LocationType locationType = StartLocation?.Type;
1941 if (locationType == null)
1942 {
1943 locationType = LocationType.Prefabs.GetRandom(Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
1944 if (ruinGenerationParams.AllowedLocationTypes.Any())
1945 {
1946 locationType = LocationType.Prefabs.Where(lt =>
1947 ruinGenerationParams.AllowedLocationTypes.Any(allowedType =>
1948 allowedType == "any" || lt.Identifier == allowedType)).GetRandom(Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
1949 }
1950 }
1951
1952 var ruin = new Ruin(this, ruinGenerationParams, locationType, ruinPos, mirror);
1953 Ruins.Add(ruin);
1954 var tooClose = GetTooCloseCells(ruinPos.ToVector2(), Math.Max(ruin.Area.Width, ruin.Area.Height) * 4);
1955
1956 foreach (VoronoiCell cell in tooClose)
1957 {
1958 if (cell.CellType == CellType.Empty) { continue; }
1959 if (ExtraWalls.Any(w => w.Cells.Contains(cell))) { continue; }
1960 foreach (GraphEdge e in cell.Edges)
1961 {
1962 if (ruin.Area.Contains(e.Point1) || ruin.Area.Contains(e.Point2) ||
1963 MathUtils.GetLineRectangleIntersection(e.Point1, e.Point2, ruin.Area, out _))
1964 {
1965 cell.CellType = CellType.Removed;
1966 for (int x = 0; x < cellGrid.GetLength(0); x++)
1967 {
1968 for (int y = 0; y < cellGrid.GetLength(1); y++)
1969 {
1970 cellGrid[x, y].Remove(cell);
1971 }
1972 }
1973 cells.Remove(cell);
1974 break;
1975 }
1976 }
1977 }
1978
1979 ruin.PathCells = CreatePathToClosestTunnel(ruin.Area.Center);
1980 }

1982 private void GenerateRuinWayPoints(Ruin ruin)
1983 {
1984 var tooClose = GetTooCloseCells(ruin.Area.Center.ToVector2(), Math.Max(ruin.Area.Width, ruin.Area.Height) * 6);
1985
1986 List<WayPoint> wayPoints = new List<WayPoint>();
1987 float outSideWaypointInterval = 500.0f;
1988 WayPoint[,] cornerWaypoint = new WayPoint[2, 2];
1989 Rectangle waypointArea = ruin.Area;
1990 waypointArea.Inflate(100, 100);
1991
1992 //generate waypoints around the ruin
1993 for (int i = 0; i < 2; i++)
1994 {
1995 for (float x = waypointArea.X + outSideWaypointInterval; x < waypointArea.Right - outSideWaypointInterval; x += outSideWaypointInterval)
1996 {
1997 var wayPoint = new WayPoint(new Vector2(x, waypointArea.Y + waypointArea.Height * i), SpawnType.Path, null)
1998 {
1999 Ruin = ruin
2000 };
2001 wayPoints.Add(wayPoint);
2002 if (x == waypointArea.X + outSideWaypointInterval)
2003 {
2004 cornerWaypoint[i, 0] = wayPoint;
2005 }
2006 else
2007 {
2008 wayPoint.ConnectTo(wayPoints[wayPoints.Count - 2]);
2009 }
2010 }
2011 cornerWaypoint[i, 1] = wayPoints[wayPoints.Count - 1];
2012 }
2013
2014 for (int i = 0; i < 2; i++)
2015 {
2016 WayPoint wayPoint = null;
2017 for (float y = waypointArea.Y; y < waypointArea.Y + waypointArea.Height; y += outSideWaypointInterval)
2018 {
2019 wayPoint = new WayPoint(new Vector2(waypointArea.X + waypointArea.Width * i, y), SpawnType.Path, null)
2020 {
2021 Ruin = ruin
2022 };
2023 wayPoints.Add(wayPoint);
2024 if (y == waypointArea.Y)
2025 {
2026 wayPoint.ConnectTo(cornerWaypoint[0, i]);
2027 }
2028 else
2029 {
2030 wayPoint.ConnectTo(wayPoints[wayPoints.Count - 2]);
2031 }
2032 }
2033 wayPoint.ConnectTo(cornerWaypoint[1, i]);
2034 }
2035
2036 //remove waypoints that are inside walls
2037 for (int i = wayPoints.Count - 1; i >= 0; i--)
2038 {
2039 WayPoint wp = wayPoints[i];
2040 var overlappingCell = tooClose.Find(c => c.CellType != CellType.Removed && c.IsPointInside(wp.WorldPosition));
2041 if (overlappingCell == null) { continue; }
2042 if (wp.linkedTo.Count > 1)
2043 {
2044 WayPoint linked1 = wp.linkedTo[0] as WayPoint;
2045 WayPoint linked2 = wp.linkedTo[1] as WayPoint;
2046 linked1.ConnectTo(linked2);
2047 }
2048 wp.Remove();
2049 wayPoints.RemoveAt(i);
2050 }
2051
2052 Debug.Assert(wayPoints.Any(), "Couldn't generate waypoints around ruins.");
2053
2054 //connect ruin entrances to the outside waypoints
2055 foreach (Gap g in Gap.GapList)
2056 {
2057 if (g.Submarine != ruin.Submarine || g.IsRoomToRoom || g.linkedTo.Count == 0) { continue; }
2058 var gapWaypoint = WayPoint.WayPointList.Find(wp => wp.ConnectedGap == g);
2059 if (gapWaypoint == null) { continue; }
2060
2061 //place another waypoint in front of the entrance
2062 Vector2 entranceDir = Vector2.Zero;
2063 if (g.IsHorizontal)
2064 {
2065 entranceDir = Vector2.UnitX * 2 * Math.Sign(g.WorldPosition.X - g.linkedTo[0].WorldPosition.X);
2066 }
2067 else
2068 {
2069 entranceDir = Vector2.UnitY * 2 * Math.Sign(g.WorldPosition.Y - g.linkedTo[0].WorldPosition.Y);
2070 }
2071 var entranceWayPoint = new WayPoint(g.WorldPosition + entranceDir * 64.0f, SpawnType.Path, null)
2072 {
2073 Ruin = ruin
2074 };
2075 entranceWayPoint.ConnectTo(gapWaypoint);
2076 var closestWp = FindClosestWayPoint(entranceWayPoint.WorldPosition, wayPoints, (wp) =>
2077 {
2078 return Submarine.PickBody(
2079 ConvertUnits.ToSimUnits(wp.WorldPosition),
2080 ConvertUnits.ToSimUnits(entranceWayPoint.WorldPosition), collisionCategory: Physics.CollisionLevel | Physics.CollisionWall) == null;
2081 });
2082 if (closestWp == null) { continue; }
2083 ConnectWaypoints(entranceWayPoint, closestWp, outSideWaypointInterval);
2084 }
2085
2086 //create a waypoint path from the ruin to the closest tunnel
2087 WayPoint prevWp = FindClosestWayPoint(ruin.PathCells.First().Center, wayPoints, (wp) =>
2088 {
2089 return Submarine.PickBody(
2090 ConvertUnits.ToSimUnits(wp.WorldPosition),
2091 ConvertUnits.ToSimUnits(ruin.PathCells.First().Center), collisionCategory: Physics.CollisionLevel | Physics.CollisionWall) == null;
2092 });
2093 if (prevWp != null)
2094 {
2095 for (int i = 0; i < ruin.PathCells.Count; i++)
2096 {
2097 var connectingEdge = i > 0 ? ruin.PathCells[i].Edges.Find(e => e.AdjacentCell(ruin.PathCells[i]) == ruin.PathCells[i - 1]) : null;
2098 if (connectingEdge != null)
2099 {
2100 var edgeWayPoint = new WayPoint(connectingEdge.Center, SpawnType.Path, submarine: null);
2101 ConnectWaypoints(prevWp, edgeWayPoint, outSideWaypointInterval);
2102 prevWp = edgeWayPoint;
2103 }
2104 var newWaypoint = new WayPoint(ruin.PathCells[i].Center, SpawnType.Path, submarine: null);
2105 ConnectWaypoints(prevWp, newWaypoint, outSideWaypointInterval);
2106 prevWp = newWaypoint;
2107 }
2108 var closestPathPoint = FindClosestWayPoint(prevWp.WorldPosition, Tunnels.SelectMany(t => t.WayPoints));
2109 ConnectWaypoints(prevWp, closestPathPoint, outSideWaypointInterval);
2110 }

2113 private Point FindPosAwayFromMainPath(double minDistance, bool asCloseAsPossible, Rectangle? limits = null)
2114 {
2115 var pointsAboveBottom = distanceField.FindAll(d => d.point.Y > GetBottomPosition(d.point.X).Y + minDistance);
2116 if (pointsAboveBottom.Count == 0)
2117 {
2118 DebugConsole.ThrowError("Error in FindPosAwayFromMainPath: no valid positions above the bottom of the sea floor. Has the position of the sea floor been set too high up?");
2119 return distanceField[Rand.Int(distanceField.Count, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient)].point;
2120 }
2121
2122 var validPoints = pointsAboveBottom.FindAll(d => d.distance >= minDistance && (limits == null || limits.Value.Contains(d.point)));
2123 if (!validPoints.Any())
2124 {
2125 DebugConsole.AddWarning("Failed to find a valid position far enough from the main path. Choosing the furthest possible position.\n" + Environment.StackTrace);
2126 if (limits != null)
2127 {
2128 //try choosing something within the specified limits
2129 validPoints = pointsAboveBottom.FindAll(d => limits.Value.Contains(d.point));
2130 }
2131 if (!validPoints.Any())
2132 {
2133 //couldn't find anything, let's just go with the furthest one
2134 validPoints = pointsAboveBottom;
2135 }
2136 (Point position, double distance) furthestPoint = validPoints.First();
2137 foreach (var point in validPoints)
2138 {
2139 if (point.distance > furthestPoint.distance)
2140 {
2141 furthestPoint = point;
2142 }
2143 }
2144 return furthestPoint.position;
2145 }
2146
2147 if (asCloseAsPossible)
2148 {
2149 if (!validPoints.Any()) { validPoints = distanceField; }
2150 (Point position, double distance) closestPoint = validPoints.First();
2151 foreach (var point in validPoints)
2152 {
2153 if (point.distance < closestPoint.distance)
2154 {
2155 closestPoint = point;
2156 }
2157 }
2158 return closestPoint.position;
2159 }
2160 else
2161 {
2162 return validPoints[Rand.Int(validPoints.Count, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient)].point;
2163 }
2164 }

2167 {

2191
2192 void addPoint(int x, int y)
2193 {
2194 Point point = new Point(x, y);
2195 double shortestDistSqr = double.PositiveInfinity;
2196 foreach (Tunnel tunnel in Tunnels)
2197 {
2198 for (int i = 1; i < tunnel.Nodes.Count; i++)
2199 {
2200 shortestDistSqr = Math.Min(shortestDistSqr, MathUtils.LineSegmentToPointDistanceSquared(tunnel.Nodes[i - 1], tunnel.Nodes[i], point));
2201 }
2202 }
2203 if (ruinPositions != null)
2204 {
2205 int ruinSize = 10000;
2206 foreach (Point ruinPos in ruinPositions)
2207 {
2208 double xDiff = Math.Abs(point.X - ruinPos.X);
2209 double yDiff = Math.Abs(point.Y - ruinPos.Y);
2210 if (xDiff < ruinSize && yDiff < ruinSize)
2211 {
2212 shortestDistSqr = 0.0f;
2213 }
2214 else
2215 {
2216 shortestDistSqr = Math.Min(xDiff * xDiff + yDiff * yDiff, shortestDistSqr);
2217 }
2218 }
2219 }
2220 shortestDistSqr = Math.Min(shortestDistSqr, MathUtils.DistanceSquared((double)point.X, (double)point.Y, (double)startPosition.X, (double)startPosition.Y));
2221 shortestDistSqr = Math.Min(shortestDistSqr, MathUtils.DistanceSquared((double)point.X, (double)point.Y, (double)startExitPosition.X, (double)borders.Bottom));
2222 shortestDistSqr = Math.Min(shortestDistSqr, MathUtils.DistanceSquared((double)point.X, (double)point.Y, (double)endPosition.X, (double)endPosition.Y));
2223 shortestDistSqr = Math.Min(shortestDistSqr, MathUtils.DistanceSquared((double)point.X, (double)point.Y, (double)endExitPosition.X, (double)borders.Bottom));
2224 distanceField.Add((point, Math.Sqrt(shortestDistSqr)));
2225 }
2226 }

2274 private DestructibleLevelWall CreateIceSpire(List<GraphEdge> usedSpireEdges)
2275 {
2276 const float maxLength = 15000.0f;
2277 float minEdgeLength = 100.0f;
2278 var mainPathPos = PositionsOfInterest.GetRandom(pos => pos.PositionType == PositionType.MainPath, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
2279 double closestDistSqr = double.PositiveInfinity;
2280 GraphEdge closestEdge = null;
2281 VoronoiCell closestCell = null;
2282 foreach (VoronoiCell cell in cells)
2283 {
2284 if (cell.CellType != CellType.Solid) { continue; }
2285 foreach (GraphEdge edge in cell.Edges)
2286 {
2287 if (!edge.IsSolid || usedSpireEdges.Contains(edge) || edge.NextToCave) { continue; }
2288 //don't spawn spires near the start/end of the level
2289 if (edge.Center.Y > Size.Y / 2 && (edge.Center.X < Size.X * 0.3f || edge.Center.X > Size.X * 0.7f)) { continue; }
2290 if (Vector2.DistanceSquared(edge.Center, StartPosition) < maxLength * maxLength) { continue; }
2291 if (Vector2.DistanceSquared(edge.Center, EndPosition) < maxLength * maxLength) { continue; }
2292 //don't spawn on very long or very short edges
2293 float edgeLengthSqr = Vector2.DistanceSquared(edge.Point1, edge.Point2);
2294 if (edgeLengthSqr > 1000.0f * 1000.0f || edgeLengthSqr < minEdgeLength * minEdgeLength) { continue; }
2295 //don't spawn on edges facing away from the main path
2296 if (Vector2.Dot(Vector2.Normalize(mainPathPos.Position.ToVector2()) - edge.Center, edge.GetNormal(cell)) < 0.5f) { continue; }
2297 double distSqr = MathUtils.DistanceSquared(edge.Center.X, edge.Center.Y, mainPathPos.Position.X, mainPathPos.Position.Y);
2298 if (distSqr < closestDistSqr)
2299 {
2300 closestDistSqr = distSqr;
2301 closestEdge = edge;
2302 closestCell = cell;
2303 }
2304 }
2305 }
2306
2307 if (closestEdge == null) { return null; }
2308
2309 usedSpireEdges.Add(closestEdge);
2310
2311 Vector2 edgeNormal = closestEdge.GetNormal(closestCell);
2312 float spireLength = (float)Math.Min(Math.Sqrt(closestDistSqr), maxLength);
2313 spireLength *= MathHelper.Lerp(0.3f, 1.5f, Difficulty / 100.0f);
2314
2315 Vector2 extrudedPoint1 = closestEdge.Point1 + edgeNormal * spireLength * Rand.Range(0.8f, 1.0f, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
2316 Vector2 extrudedPoint2 = closestEdge.Point2 + edgeNormal * spireLength * Rand.Range(0.8f, 1.0f, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
2317 List<Vector2> vertices = new List<Vector2>()
2318 {
2319 closestEdge.Point1,
2320 extrudedPoint1 + (extrudedPoint2 - extrudedPoint1) * Rand.Range(0.3f, 0.45f, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient),
2321 extrudedPoint2 + (extrudedPoint1 - extrudedPoint2) * Rand.Range(0.3f, 0.45f, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient),
2322 closestEdge.Point2,
2323 };
2324 Vector2 center = Vector2.Zero;
2325 vertices.ForEach(v => center += v);
2326 center /= vertices.Count;
2327 DestructibleLevelWall spire = new DestructibleLevelWall(vertices.Select(v => v - center).ToList(), Color.White, this, health: 100.0f, giftWrap: true);
2328#if CLIENT
2329 //make the edge at the bottom of the spire non-solid
2330 foreach (GraphEdge edge in spire.Cells[0].Edges)
2331 {
2332 if ((edge.Point1.NearlyEquals(closestEdge.Point1 - center) && edge.Point2.NearlyEquals(closestEdge.Point2 - center)) ||
2333 (edge.Point1.NearlyEquals(closestEdge.Point2 - center) && edge.Point2.NearlyEquals(closestEdge.Point1 - center)))
2334 {
2335 edge.IsSolid = false;
2336 break;
2337 }
2338 }
2339 spire.GenerateVertices();
2340#endif
2341 spire.Body.Position = ConvertUnits.ToSimUnits(center);
2342 spire.Body.BodyType = BodyType.Static;
2343 spire.Body.FixedRotation = true;
2344 spire.Body.IgnoreGravity = true;
2345 spire.Body.Mass *= 10.0f;
2346 spire.Cells.ForEach(c => c.Translation = center);
2347 spire.WallDamageOnTouch = 50.0f;
2348 return spire;
2349 }

2521 reachedLastNode = !CalculatePositionOnPath();
2522 var id = Tunnels.IndexOf(tunnel) + ":" + nextPathPointId++;
2523 var spawnChance = tunnel.Type == TunnelType.Cave || tunnel.ParentTunnel?.Type == TunnelType.Cave ?
2524 GenerationParams.CaveResourceSpawnChance : GenerationParams.ResourceSpawnChance;
2525 var containsResources = true;
2526 if (spawnChance < 1.0f)
2527 {
2528 var spawnPointRoll = Rand.Range(0.0f, 1.0f, sync: Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
2529 containsResources = spawnPointRoll <= spawnChance;
2530 }
2531 var tunnelType = tunnel.Type;
2532 if (tunnel.ParentTunnel != null && tunnel.ParentTunnel.Type == TunnelType.Cave) { tunnelType = TunnelType.Cave; }
2533 PathPoints.Add(new PathPoint(id, positionOnPath, containsResources, tunnel.Type));
2534
2535 bool CalculatePositionOnPath(float checkedDist = 0.0f)
2536 {
2537 if (nextNodeIndex >= tunnel.Nodes.Count) { return false; }
2538 var distToNextNode = Vector2.Distance(positionOnPath, tunnel.Nodes[nextNodeIndex].ToVector2());
2539 var lerpAmount = (distance - checkedDist) / distToNextNode;
2540 if (lerpAmount <= 1.0f)
2541 {
2542 positionOnPath = Vector2.Lerp(positionOnPath, tunnel.Nodes[nextNodeIndex].ToVector2(), lerpAmount);
2543 return true;
2544 }
2545 else
2546 {
2547 positionOnPath = tunnel.Nodes[nextNodeIndex++].ToVector2();
2548 return CalculatePositionOnPath(checkedDist + distToNextNode);
2549 }
2550 }
2551 } while (!reachedLastNode && Vector2.DistanceSquared(positionOnPath, lastNodePos) > (intervalRange.Y * intervalRange.Y));
2552 }
2553
2554 int itemCount = 0;
2555 Identifier[] exclusiveResourceTags = new Identifier[2] { "ore".ToIdentifier(), "plant".ToIdentifier() };
2556
2557 // Create first cluster for each spawn point
2558 foreach (var pathPoint in PathPoints.Where(p => p.ShouldContainResources))
2559 {
2560 if (itemCount >= GenerationParams.ItemCount) { break; }
2561 GenerateFirstCluster(pathPoint);
2562 }
2563
2564 // Don't try to spawn more resource clusters for points
2565 // for which the initial cluster could not be spawned
2566 PathPoints.Where(p => p.ShouldContainResources && p.ClusterLocations.Count == 0)
2567 .ForEach(p => p.ShouldContainResources = false);
2568
2569 var excludedPathPointIds = new List<string>();
2570 while (itemCount < GenerationParams.ItemCount)
2571 {
2572 var availablePathPoints = PathPoints.Where(p =>
2573 p.ShouldContainResources && p.NextClusterProbability > 0 &&
2574 !excludedPathPointIds.Contains(p.Id)).ToList();
2575
2576 if (availablePathPoints.None()) { break; }
2577
2578 var pathPoint = ToolBox.SelectWeightedRandom(
2579 availablePathPoints,
2580 availablePathPoints.Select(p => p.NextClusterProbability).ToList(),
2581 Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
2582
2583 GenerateAdditionalCluster(pathPoint);
2584 }
2585
2586 // If none of the point set to contain resources can take more resources,
2587 // but we still haven't reached the item count set in the generation parameters...
2588 while (itemCount < GenerationParams.ItemCount)
2589 {
2590 // We need to start filling some of the path points previously set to not contain resources
2591 Func<PathPoint, bool> availablePathPoints = p => !excludedPathPointIds.Contains(p.Id) && p.ClusterLocations.None();
2592 if (PathPoints.None(availablePathPoints)) { break; }
2593 var pathPoint = PathPoints.GetRandom(availablePathPoints, randSync: Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
2594 if (!GenerateFirstCluster(pathPoint))
2595 {
2596 excludedPathPointIds.Add(pathPoint.Id);
2597 continue;
2598 }
2599 while (pathPoint.NextClusterProbability > 0)
2600 {
2601 if (!GenerateAdditionalCluster(pathPoint)) { break; }
2602 }
2603 pathPoint.ShouldContainResources = pathPoint.ClusterLocations.Any();
2604 }
2605
2606#if DEBUG
2607 DebugConsole.NewMessage("Level resources spawned: " + itemCount + "\n" +
2608 " Spawn points containing resources: " + PathPoints.Where(p => p.ClusterLocations.Any()).Count() + "/" + PathPoints.Count + "\n" +
2609 " Total value: "+ PathPoints.Sum(p => p.ClusterLocations.Sum(c => c.Resources.Sum(r => r.Prefab.DefaultPrice?.Price ?? 0)))+" mk");
2610 if (AbyssResources.Count > 0)
2611 {
2612
2613 DebugConsole.NewMessage("Abyss resources spawned: " + AbyssResources.Sum(a => a.Resources.Count) + "\n" +
2614 " Total value: " + AbyssResources.Sum(c => c.Resources.Sum(r => r.Prefab.DefaultPrice?.Price ?? 0)) + " mk");
2615 }
2616#endif
2617
2618 DebugConsole.Log("Level resources generated");
2619
2620 bool GenerateFirstCluster(PathPoint pathPoint)
2621 {
2622 var intervalRange = pathPoint.TunnelType != TunnelType.Cave ?
2623 GenerationParams.ResourceIntervalRange : GenerationParams.CaveResourceIntervalRange;
2624 allValidLocations.Sort((x, y) =>
2625 Vector2.DistanceSquared(pathPoint.Position, x.EdgeCenter)
2626 .CompareTo(Vector2.DistanceSquared(pathPoint.Position, y.EdgeCenter)));
2627 var selectedLocationIndex = -1;
2628 var generatedCluster = false;
2629 for (int i = 0; i < allValidLocations.Count; i++)
2630 {
2631 var validLocation = allValidLocations[i];
2632 if (!IsNextToTunnelType(validLocation.Edge, pathPoint.TunnelType)) { continue; }
2633 if (validLocation.EdgeCenter.Y < AbyssArea.Bottom) { continue; }
2634 var distanceSquaredToEdge = Vector2.DistanceSquared(pathPoint.Position, validLocation.EdgeCenter);
2635 // Edge isn't too far from the path point
2636 if (distanceSquaredToEdge > 3.0f * (intervalRange.Y * intervalRange.Y)) { continue; }
2637 // Edge is closer to the path point than the cell center
2638 if (distanceSquaredToEdge > Vector2.DistanceSquared(pathPoint.Position, validLocation.Cell.Center)) { continue; }
2639
2640 var validComparedToOtherPathPoints = true;
2641 // Make sure this path point is closest to 'validLocation'
2642 foreach (var anotherPathPoint in PathPoints)
2643 {
2644 if (anotherPathPoint.Id == pathPoint.Id) { continue; }
2645 if (Vector2.DistanceSquared(anotherPathPoint.Position, validLocation.EdgeCenter) < distanceSquaredToEdge)
2646 {
2647 validComparedToOtherPathPoints = false;
2648 break;
2649 }
2650 }
2651
2652 foreach (var anotherPathPoint in PathPoints.Where(p => p.Id != pathPoint.Id && p.ClusterLocations.Any()))
2653 {
2654 if (!validComparedToOtherPathPoints) { break; }
2655 foreach (var c in pathPoint.ClusterLocations)
2656 {
2657 if (IsInvalidComparedToExistingLocation())
2658 {
2659 validComparedToOtherPathPoints = false;
2660 break;
2661 }
2662
2663 bool IsInvalidComparedToExistingLocation()
2664 {
2665 if (c.Equals(validLocation)) { return true; }
2666 // If there is a previously spawned cluster too near
2667 if (Vector2.DistanceSquared(c.EdgeCenter, validLocation.EdgeCenter) > (intervalRange.X * intervalRange.X)) { return true; }
2668 // If there is a line from a previous path point to one of its existing cluster locations
2669 // which intersects with the line from this path point to the new possible cluster location
2670 if (MathUtils.LinesIntersect(anotherPathPoint.Position, c.EdgeCenter, pathPoint.Position, validLocation.EdgeCenter)) { return true; }
2671 return false;
2672 }
2673 }
2674 }
2675
2676 if (!validComparedToOtherPathPoints) { continue; }
2677 generatedCluster = CreateResourceCluster(pathPoint, validLocation);
2678 selectedLocationIndex = i;
2679 break;
2680 }
2681
2682 if (selectedLocationIndex >= 0)
2683 {
2684 allValidLocations.RemoveAt(selectedLocationIndex);
2685 }
2686
2687 return generatedCluster;
2688
2689 static bool IsNextToTunnelType(GraphEdge e, TunnelType t) =>
2690 (e.NextToMainPath && t == TunnelType.MainPath) ||
2691 (e.NextToSidePath && t == TunnelType.SidePath) ||
2692 (e.NextToCave && t == TunnelType.Cave);
2693 }
2694
2695 bool GenerateAdditionalCluster(PathPoint pathPoint)
2696 {
2697 var validLocations = new List<ClusterLocation>();
2698 // First check only the edges of the same cell
2699 // which are connected to one of the existing edges with clusters
2700 foreach (var clusterLocation in pathPoint.ClusterLocations)
2701 {
2702 foreach (var anotherEdge in clusterLocation.Cell.Edges.Where(e => e != clusterLocation.Edge))
2703 {
2704 if (HaveConnectingEdgePoints(anotherEdge, clusterLocation.Edge))
2705 {
2706 AddIfValid(clusterLocation.Cell, anotherEdge);
2707 }
2708 }
2709 }
2710
2711 // Only check edges of adjacent cells if no valid edges were found
2712 // on any of the cells with existing clusters
2713 if (validLocations.None())
2714 {
2715 foreach (var clusterLocation in pathPoint.ClusterLocations)
2716 {
2717 foreach (var anotherEdge in clusterLocation.Cell.Edges.Where(e => e != clusterLocation.Edge))
2718 {
2719 var adjacentCell = anotherEdge.AdjacentCell(clusterLocation.Cell);
2720 if (adjacentCell == null) { continue; }
2721 foreach (var adjacentCellEdge in adjacentCell.Edges.Where(e => e != anotherEdge))
2722 {
2723 if (HaveConnectingEdgePoints(adjacentCellEdge, clusterLocation.Edge))
2724 {
2725 AddIfValid(adjacentCell, adjacentCellEdge);
2726 }
2727 }
2728 }
2729 }
2730 }
2731
2732 if (validLocations.Any())
2733 {
2734 var location = validLocations.GetRandom(randSync: Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
2735 if (CreateResourceCluster(pathPoint, location))
2736 {
2737 var i = allValidLocations.FindIndex(l => l.Equals(location));
2738 if (i >= 0)
2739 {
2740 allValidLocations.RemoveAt(i);
2741 }
2742 return true;
2743 }
2744 else
2745 {
2746 excludedPathPointIds.Add(pathPoint.Id);
2747 return false;
2748 }
2749 }
2750 else
2751 {
2752 excludedPathPointIds.Add(pathPoint.Id);
2753 return false;
2754 }
2755
2756 static bool HaveConnectingEdgePoints(GraphEdge e1, GraphEdge e2) =>
2757 e1.Point1.NearlyEquals(e2.Point1) || e1.Point1.NearlyEquals(e2.Point2) ||
2758 e1.Point2.NearlyEquals(e2.Point1) || e1.Point2.NearlyEquals(e2.Point2);
2759
2760 void AddIfValid(VoronoiCell c, GraphEdge e)
2761 {
2762 if (IsAlreadyInList(e)) { return; }
2763 if (allValidLocations.None(l => l.Equals(c, e))) { return; }
2764 if (pathPoint.ClusterLocations.Any(cl => cl.Edge == e)) { return; }
2765 validLocations.Add(new ClusterLocation(c, e));
2766 }
2767
2768 bool IsAlreadyInList(GraphEdge edge) =>
2769 validLocations.Any(l => l.Edge == edge);
2770 }
2771
2772 bool CreateResourceCluster(PathPoint pathPoint, ClusterLocation location)
2773 {
2774 if (location.Cell == null || location.Edge == null) { return false; }
2775
2776 ItemPrefab selectedPrefab;
2777 if (pathPoint.ClusterLocations.Count == 0)
2778 {
2779 selectedPrefab = ToolBox.SelectWeightedRandom(
2780 levelResources.Select(it => it.itemPrefab).ToList(),
2781 levelResources.Select(it => it.commonness).ToList(),
2782 Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
2783 selectedPrefab.Tags.ForEach(t =>
2784 {
2785 if (exclusiveResourceTags.Contains(t))
2786 {
2787 pathPoint.ResourceTags.Add(t);
2788 }
2789 });
2790 }
2791 else
2792 {
2793 var filteredResources = levelResources.Where(it =>
2794 !pathPoint.ResourceIds.Contains(it.itemPrefab.Identifier) &&
2795 pathPoint.ResourceTags.Any() && it.itemPrefab.Tags.Any(t => pathPoint.ResourceTags.Contains(t)));
2796 selectedPrefab = ToolBox.SelectWeightedRandom(
2797 filteredResources.Select(it => it.itemPrefab).ToList(),
2798 filteredResources.Select(it => it.commonness).ToList(),
2799 Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
2800 }
2801
2802 if (selectedPrefab == null) { return false; }
2803
2804 // Create resources for the cluster
2805 var commonness = levelResources.First(r => r.itemPrefab == selectedPrefab).commonness;
2806 var lerpAmount = MathUtils.InverseLerp(minCommonness, maxCommonness, commonness);
2807 var maxClusterSize = (int)MathHelper.Lerp(GenerationParams.ResourceClusterSizeRange.X, GenerationParams.ResourceClusterSizeRange.Y, lerpAmount);
2808 var maxFitOnEdge = GetMaxResourcesOnEdge(selectedPrefab, location, out var edgeLength);
2809 maxClusterSize = Math.Min(maxClusterSize, maxFitOnEdge);
2810 if (itemCount + maxClusterSize > GenerationParams.ItemCount)
2811 {
2812 maxClusterSize += GenerationParams.ItemCount - (itemCount + maxClusterSize);
2813 }
2814
2815 if (maxClusterSize < 1) { return false; }
2816
2817 var minClusterSize = Math.Min(GenerationParams.ResourceClusterSizeRange.X, maxClusterSize);
2818 var resourcesInCluster = maxClusterSize == 1 ? 1 : Rand.Range(minClusterSize, maxClusterSize + 1, sync: Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
2819
2820 if (resourcesInCluster < 1) { return false; }
2821
2822 PlaceResources(selectedPrefab, resourcesInCluster, location, out var placedResources, edgeLength: edgeLength);
2823 itemCount += resourcesInCluster;
2824 location.InitializeResources();
2825 location.Resources.AddRange(placedResources);
2826 pathPoint.ClusterLocations.Add(location);
2827 pathPoint.ResourceIds.Add(selectedPrefab.Identifier);
2828
2829 return true;
2830 }
2831
2832 int GetMaxResourcesOnEdge(ItemPrefab resourcePrefab, ClusterLocation location, out float edgeLength)
2833 {
2834 edgeLength = 0.0f;
2835 if (location.Cell == null || location.Edge == null) { return 0; }
2836 edgeLength = Vector2.Distance(location.Edge.Point1, location.Edge.Point2);
2837 return (int)Math.Floor(edgeLength / ((1.0f - maxResourceOverlap) * resourcePrefab.Size.X));
2838 }
2839 }

2842 public List<Item> GenerateMissionResources(ItemPrefab prefab, int requiredAmount, out float rotation)
2843 {
2844 var allValidLocations = GetAllValidClusterLocations();
2845 var placedResources = new List<Item>();
2846 rotation = 0.0f;
2847 if (allValidLocations.None()) { return placedResources; } // TODO: WHAT?!
2848
2849 for (int i = allValidLocations.Count - 1; i >= 0; i--)
2850 {
2851 var location = allValidLocations[i];
2852 var locationHasResources = PathPoints.Any(p =>
2853 p.ClusterLocations.Any(c =>
2854 c.Equals(location) &&
2855 c.Resources.Any(r => r != null && !r.Removed &&
2856 (!(r.GetComponent<Holdable>() is Holdable h) || (h.Attachable && h.Attached)))));
2857 if (locationHasResources)
2858 {
2859 allValidLocations.RemoveAt(i);
2860 }
2861 }
2862
2863 var positionType = PositionType.MainPath;
2864 if (PositionsOfInterest.Any(p => p.PositionType == PositionType.Cave))
2865 {
2866 positionType = PositionType.Cave;
2867 if (allValidLocations.Any(l => l.Edge.NextToCave))
2868 {
2869 allValidLocations.RemoveAll(l => !l.Edge.NextToCave);
2870 }
2871 }
2872 else if (PositionsOfInterest.Any(p => p.PositionType == PositionType.SidePath))
2873 {
2874 positionType = PositionType.SidePath;
2875 if (allValidLocations.Any(l => l.Edge.NextToSidePath))
2876 {
2877 allValidLocations.RemoveAll(l => !l.Edge.NextToSidePath);
2878 }
2879 }
2880
2881 var poi = PositionsOfInterest.GetRandom(p => p.PositionType == positionType, randSync: Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
2882 var poiPos = poi.Position.ToVector2();
2883 allValidLocations.Sort((x, y) => Vector2.DistanceSquared(poiPos, x.EdgeCenter)
2884 .CompareTo(Vector2.DistanceSquared(poiPos, y.EdgeCenter)));
2885 var maxResourceOverlap = 0.4f;
2886 var selectedLocation = allValidLocations.FirstOrDefault(l =>
2887 Vector2.Distance(l.Edge.Point1, l.Edge.Point2) is float edgeLength &&
2888 requiredAmount <= (int)Math.Floor(edgeLength / ((1.0f - maxResourceOverlap) * prefab.Size.X)));
2889 if (selectedLocation.Edge == null)
2890 {
2891 //couldn't find a long enough edge, find the largest one
2892 float longestEdge = 0.0f;
2893 foreach (var validLocation in allValidLocations)
2894 {
2895 if (Vector2.Distance(validLocation.Edge.Point1, validLocation.Edge.Point2) is float edgeLength && edgeLength > longestEdge)
2896 {
2897 selectedLocation = validLocation;
2898 longestEdge = edgeLength;
2899 }
2900 }
2901 }
2902 if (selectedLocation.Edge == null)
2903 {
2904 throw new Exception("Failed to find a suitable level wall edge to place level resources on.");
2905 }
2906 PlaceResources(prefab, requiredAmount, selectedLocation, out placedResources);
2907 var edgeNormal = selectedLocation.Edge.GetNormal(selectedLocation.Cell);
2908 rotation = MathHelper.ToDegrees(-MathUtils.VectorToAngle(edgeNormal) + MathHelper.PiOver2);
2909 return placedResources;
2910 }

2912 private List<ClusterLocation> GetAllValidClusterLocations()
2913 {
2914 var subBorders = new List<Rectangle>();
2915 Wrecks.ForEach(w => AddBordersToList(w));
2916 AddBordersToList(BeaconStation);
2917
2918 var locations = new List<ClusterLocation>();
2919 foreach (var c in GetAllCells())
2920 {
2921 if (c.CellType != CellType.Solid) { continue; }
2922 foreach (var e in c.Edges)
2923 {
2924 if (IsValidEdge(e))
2925 {
2926 locations.Add(new ClusterLocation(c, e));
2927 }
2928 }
2929 }
2930 return locations;

2932 void AddBordersToList(Submarine s)
2933 {
2934 if (s == null) { return; }
2935 var rect = Submarine.AbsRect(s.WorldPosition, s.Borders.Size.ToVector2());
2936 subBorders.Add(rect);
2937 }
2938
2939 bool IsValidEdge(GraphEdge e)
2940 {
2941 if (!e.IsSolid) { return false; }
2942 if (e.OutsideLevel) { return false; }
2943 var eCenter = e.Center;
2944 if (IsBlockedByWreckOrBeacon()) { return false; }
2945 if (IsBlockedByWall()) { return false; }
2946 return true;
2947
2948 bool IsBlockedByWreckOrBeacon()
2949 {
2950 foreach (var r in subBorders)
2951 {
2952 if (Submarine.RectContains(r, e.Point1)) { return true; }
2953 if (Submarine.RectContains(r, e.Point2)) { return true; }
2954 if (Submarine.RectContains(r, eCenter)) { return true; }
2955 }
2956 return false;
2957 }
2958
2959 bool IsBlockedByWall()
2960 {
2961 foreach (var w in ExtraWalls)
2962 {
2963 foreach (var c in w.Cells)
2964 {
2965 if (c.IsPointInside(eCenter)) { return true; }
2966 if (c.IsPointInside(eCenter - 100 * e.GetNormal(c))) { return true; }
2967 if (c.Edges.Any(extraWallEdge => extraWallEdge == e)) { return true; }
2968 }
2969 }
2970 return false;
2971 }
2972 }

2975 private void PlaceResources(ItemPrefab resourcePrefab, int resourceCount, ClusterLocation location, out List<Item> placedResources,
2976 float? edgeLength = null, float maxResourceOverlap = 0.4f)
2977 {
2978 edgeLength ??= Vector2.Distance(location.Edge.Point1, location.Edge.Point2);
2979 Vector2 edgeDir = (location.Edge.Point2 - location.Edge.Point1) / edgeLength.Value;
2980 var minResourceOverlap = -((edgeLength.Value - (resourceCount * resourcePrefab.Size.X)) / (resourceCount * resourcePrefab.Size.X));
2981 minResourceOverlap = Math.Max(minResourceOverlap, 0.0f);
2982 var lerpAmounts = new float[resourceCount];
2983 lerpAmounts[0] = 0.0f;
2984 var lerpAmount = 0.0f;
2985 for (int i = 1; i < resourceCount; i++)
2986 {
2987 var overlap = Rand.Range(minResourceOverlap, maxResourceOverlap, sync: Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
2988 lerpAmount += ((1.0f - overlap) * resourcePrefab.Size.X) / edgeLength.Value;
2989 lerpAmounts[i] = Math.Clamp(lerpAmount, 0.0f, 1.0f);
2990 }
2991 var startOffset = Rand.Range(0.0f, 1.0f - lerpAmount, sync: Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
2992 placedResources = new List<Item>();
2993 for (int i = 0; i < resourceCount; i++)
2994 {
2995 Vector2 selectedPos = Vector2.Lerp(location.Edge.Point1 + edgeDir * resourcePrefab.Size.X / 2, location.Edge.Point2 - edgeDir * resourcePrefab.Size.X / 2, startOffset + lerpAmounts[i]);
2996 var item = new Item(resourcePrefab, selectedPos, submarine: null);
2997 Vector2 edgeNormal = location.Edge.GetNormal(location.Cell);
2998 float moveAmount = (item.body == null ? item.Rect.Height / 2 : ConvertUnits.ToDisplayUnits(item.body.GetMaxExtent() * 0.7f));
2999 moveAmount += (item.GetComponent<LevelResource>()?.RandomOffsetFromWall ?? 0.0f) * Rand.Range(-0.5f, 0.5f, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
3000 item.Move(edgeNormal * moveAmount, ignoreContacts: true);
3001 if (item.GetComponent<Holdable>() is Holdable h)
3002 {
3003 h.AttachToWall();
3004#if CLIENT
3005 item.Rotation = MathHelper.ToDegrees(-MathUtils.VectorToAngle(edgeNormal) + MathHelper.PiOver2);
3006#endif
3007 }
3008 else if (item.body != null)
3009 {
3010 item.body.SetTransformIgnoreContacts(item.body.SimPosition, MathUtils.VectorToAngle(edgeNormal) - MathHelper.PiOver2);
3011 }
3012 placedResources.Add(item);
3013 }
3014 }

3016 public Vector2 GetRandomItemPos(PositionType spawnPosType, float randomSpread, float minDistFromSubs, float offsetFromWall = 10.0f, Func<InterestingPosition, bool> filter = null)
3017 {
3018 if (!PositionsOfInterest.Any())
3019 {
3020 return new Vector2(Size.X / 2, Size.Y / 2);
3021 }
3022
3023 Vector2 position = Vector2.Zero;
3024
3025 int tries = 0;
3026 do
3027 {
3028 TryGetInterestingPosition(true, spawnPosType, minDistFromSubs, out Vector2 startPos, filter);
3029
3030 Vector2 offset = Rand.Vector(Rand.Range(0.0f, randomSpread, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient), Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
3031 if (!cells.Any(c => c.IsPointInside(startPos + offset)))
3032 {
3033 startPos += offset;
3034 }
3035
3036 Vector2 endPos = startPos - Vector2.UnitY * Size.Y;
3037
3038 if (Submarine.PickBody(
3039 ConvertUnits.ToSimUnits(startPos),
3040 ConvertUnits.ToSimUnits(endPos),
3041 ExtraWalls.Where(w => w.Body?.BodyType == BodyType.Dynamic || w is DestructibleLevelWall).Select(w => w.Body).Union(Submarine.Loaded.Where(s => s.Info.Type == SubmarineType.Player).Select(s => s.PhysicsBody.FarseerBody)),
3042 Physics.CollisionLevel | Physics.CollisionWall) != null)
3043 {
3044 position = ConvertUnits.ToDisplayUnits(Submarine.LastPickedPosition) + Vector2.Normalize(startPos - endPos) * offsetFromWall;
3045 break;
3046 }
3047
3048 tries++;
3049
3050 if (tries == 10)
3051 {
3052 position = startPos;
3053 }
3054
3055 } while (tries < 10);
3056
3057 return position;
3058 }

3074 public bool TryGetInterestingPosition(bool useSyncedRand, PositionType positionType, float minDistFromSubs, out Point position, Vector2 awayPoint, float minDistFromPoint = 0f, Func<InterestingPosition, bool> filter = null)
3075 {
3076 if (!PositionsOfInterest.Any())
3077 {
3078 position = new Point(Size.X / 2, Size.Y / 2);
3079 return false;
3080 }
3081
3082 List<InterestingPosition> suitablePositions = PositionsOfInterest.FindAll(p => positionType.HasFlag(p.PositionType));
3083 if (filter != null)
3084 {
3085 suitablePositions.RemoveAll(p => !filter(p));
3086 }
3087 //avoid floating ice chunks on the main path
3088 if (positionType.HasFlag(PositionType.MainPath) || positionType.HasFlag(PositionType.SidePath))
3089 {
3090 suitablePositions.RemoveAll(p => ExtraWalls.Any(w => w.Cells.Any(c => c.IsPointInside(p.Position.ToVector2()))));
3091 }
3092 if (!suitablePositions.Any())
3093 {
3094 string errorMsg = "Could not find a suitable position of interest. (PositionType: " + positionType + ", minDistFromSubs: " + minDistFromSubs + ")\n" + Environment.StackTrace.CleanupStackTrace();
3095 GameAnalyticsManager.AddErrorEventOnce("Level.TryGetInterestingPosition:PositionTypeNotFound", GameAnalyticsManager.ErrorSeverity.Error, errorMsg);
3096#if DEBUG

3184 public Vector2 GetBottomPosition(float xPosition)
3185 {
3186 int index = (int)Math.Floor(xPosition / Size.X * (bottomPositions.Count - 1));
3187 if (index < 0 || index >= bottomPositions.Count - 1) { return new Vector2(xPosition, BottomPos); }
3188

3193 float yPos = MathHelper.Lerp(bottomPositions[index].Y, bottomPositions[index + 1].Y, t);

3211 private readonly List<VoronoiCell> tempCells = new List<VoronoiCell>();
3212 public List<VoronoiCell> GetCells(Vector2 worldPos, int searchDepth = 2)
3213 {
3214 tempCells.Clear();
3215 int gridPosX = (int)Math.Floor(worldPos.X / GridCellSize);
3216 int gridPosY = (int)Math.Floor(worldPos.Y / GridCellSize);
3217
3218 int startX = Math.Max(gridPosX - searchDepth, 0);
3219 int endX = Math.Min(gridPosX + searchDepth, cellGrid.GetLength(0) - 1);
3220
3221 int startY = Math.Max(gridPosY - searchDepth, 0);
3222 int endY = Math.Min(gridPosY + searchDepth, cellGrid.GetLength(1) - 1);
3223
3224 for (int y = startY; y <= endY; y++)
3225 {
3226 for (int x = startX; x <= endX; x++)
3227 {
3228 tempCells.AddRange(cellGrid[x, y]);
3229 }
3230 }
3231
3232 foreach (LevelWall wall in ExtraWalls)
3233 {
3234 if (wall == SeaFloor)
3235 {
3236 if (SeaFloorTopPos < worldPos.Y - searchDepth * GridCellSize) { continue; }
3237 }
3238 else
3239 {
3240 if (wall is DestructibleLevelWall destructibleWall && destructibleWall.Destroyed) { continue; }
3241 bool closeEnough = false;
3242 foreach (VoronoiCell cell in wall.Cells)
3243 {
3244 if (Math.Abs(cell.Center.X - worldPos.X) < (searchDepth + 1) * GridCellSize &&
3245 Math.Abs(cell.Center.Y - worldPos.Y) < (searchDepth + 1) * GridCellSize)
3246 {
3247 closeEnough = true;
3248 break;
3249 }
3250 }
3251 if (!closeEnough) { continue; }
3252 }
3253 foreach (VoronoiCell cell in wall.Cells)
3254 {
3255 tempCells.Add(cell);
3256 }
3257 }
3258
3259 foreach (var abyssIsland in AbyssIslands)
3260 {
3261 if (abyssIsland.Area.X > worldPos.X + searchDepth * GridCellSize) { continue; }
3262 if (abyssIsland.Area.Right < worldPos.X - searchDepth * GridCellSize) { continue; }
3263 if (abyssIsland.Area.Y > worldPos.Y + searchDepth * GridCellSize) { continue; }
3264 if (abyssIsland.Area.Bottom < worldPos.Y - searchDepth * GridCellSize) { continue; }
3265
3266 tempCells.AddRange(abyssIsland.Cells);
3267 }
3268
3269 return tempCells;

3272 public VoronoiCell GetClosestCell(Vector2 worldPos)
3273 {
3274 double closestDist = double.MaxValue;

3294 private List<VoronoiCell> CreatePathToClosestTunnel(Point pos)
3295 {
3296 VoronoiCell closestPathCell = null;
3297 double closestDist = 0.0f;
3298 foreach (Tunnel tunnel in Tunnels)
3299 {
3300 if (tunnel.Type == TunnelType.Cave) { continue; }
3301 foreach (VoronoiCell cell in tunnel.Cells)
3302 {
3303 double dist = MathUtils.DistanceSquared(cell.Site.Coord.X, cell.Site.Coord.Y, pos.X, pos.Y);
3304 if (closestPathCell == null || dist < closestDist)
3305 {
3306 closestPathCell = cell;
3307 closestDist = dist;
3308 }
3309 }
3310 }
3311
3312 //cast a ray from the closest path cell towards the position and remove the cells it hits
3313 List<VoronoiCell> validCells = cells.FindAll(c => c.CellType != CellType.Empty && c.CellType != CellType.Removed);
3314 List<VoronoiCell> pathCells = new List<VoronoiCell>() { closestPathCell };
3315 foreach (VoronoiCell cell in validCells)
3316 {
3317 foreach (GraphEdge e in cell.Edges)
3318 {
3319 if (!MathUtils.LinesIntersect(closestPathCell.Center, pos.ToVector2(), e.Point1, e.Point2)) { continue; }
3320
3321 cell.CellType = CellType.Removed;
3322 for (int x = 0; x < cellGrid.GetLength(0); x++)
3323 {
3324 for (int y = 0; y < cellGrid.GetLength(1); y++)
3325 {
3326 cellGrid[x, y].Remove(cell);
3327 }
3328 }
3329 pathCells.Add(cell);
3330 cells.Remove(cell);
3331
3332 //go through the edges of this cell and find the ones that are next to a removed cell
3333 foreach (var otherEdge in cell.Edges)
3334 {
3335 var otherAdjacent = otherEdge.AdjacentCell(cell);
3336 if (otherAdjacent == null || otherAdjacent.CellType == CellType.Solid) { continue; }
3337
3338 //if the edge is very short, remove adjacent cells to prevent making the passage too narrow
3339 if (Vector2.DistanceSquared(otherEdge.Point1, otherEdge.Point2) < 500.0f * 500.0f)
3340 {
3341 foreach (GraphEdge e2 in cell.Edges)
3342 {
3343 if (e2 == otherEdge || e2 == otherEdge) { continue; }
3344 if (!MathUtils.NearlyEqual(otherEdge.Point1, e2.Point1) && !MathUtils.NearlyEqual(otherEdge.Point2, e2.Point1) && !MathUtils.NearlyEqual(otherEdge.Point2, e2.Point2))
3345 {
3346 continue;
3347 }
3348 var adjacentCell = e2.AdjacentCell(cell);
3349 if (adjacentCell == null || adjacentCell.CellType == CellType.Removed) { continue; }
3350 adjacentCell.CellType = CellType.Removed;
3351 for (int x = 0; x < cellGrid.GetLength(0); x++)
3352 {
3353 for (int y = 0; y < cellGrid.GetLength(1); y++)
3354 {
3355 cellGrid[x, y].Remove(adjacentCell);
3356 }
3357 }
3358 cells.Remove(adjacentCell);
3359 }
3360 }
3361 }
3362 break;
3363 }
3364 }
3365
3366 pathCells.Sort((c1, c2) => { return Vector2.DistanceSquared(c1.Center, pos.ToVector2()).CompareTo(Vector2.DistanceSquared(c2.Center, pos.ToVector2())); });
3367 return pathCells;
3368 }

3490 bool TryPositionSub(Rectangle subBorders, string subName, ref Vector2 spawnPoint)
3491 {
3492 positions.Add(spawnPoint);
3493 bool bottomFound = TryRaycastToBottom(subBorders, ref spawnPoint);
3494 positions.Add(spawnPoint);
3495
3496 bool leftSideBlocked = IsSideBlocked(subBorders, false);
3497 bool rightSideBlocked = IsSideBlocked(subBorders, true);
3498 int step = 5;
3499 if (rightSideBlocked && !leftSideBlocked)
3500 {
3501 bottomFound = TryMove(subBorders, ref spawnPoint, -step);
3502 }
3503 else if (leftSideBlocked && !rightSideBlocked)
3504 {
3505 bottomFound = TryMove(subBorders, ref spawnPoint, step);
3506 }
3507 else if (!bottomFound)
3508 {
3509 if (!leftSideBlocked)
3510 {
3511 bottomFound = TryMove(subBorders, ref spawnPoint, -step);
3512 }
3513 else if (!rightSideBlocked)
3514 {
3515 bottomFound = TryMove(subBorders, ref spawnPoint, step);
3516 }
3517 else
3518 {
3519 Debug.WriteLine($"Invalid position {spawnPoint}. Does not touch the ground.");
3520 return false;
3521 }
3522 }
3523 positions.Add(spawnPoint);
3524 bool isBlocked = IsBlocked(spawnPoint, subBorders.Size - new Point(step + 50));
3525 if (isBlocked)
3526 {
3527 rects.Add(ToolBox.GetWorldBounds(spawnPoint.ToPoint(), subBorders.Size));
3528 Debug.WriteLine($"Invalid position {spawnPoint}. Blocked by level walls.");
3529 }
3530 else if (!bottomFound)
3531 {
3532 Debug.WriteLine($"Invalid position {spawnPoint}. Does not touch the ground.");
3533 }
3534 else
3535 {
3536 var sp = spawnPoint;
3537 if (Wrecks.Any(w => Vector2.DistanceSquared(w.WorldPosition, sp) < minDistance * minDistance))
3538 {
3539 Debug.WriteLine($"Invalid position {spawnPoint}. Too close to other wreck(s).");
3540 return false;
3541 }
3542 }
3543 return !isBlocked && bottomFound;
3544
3545 bool TryMove(Rectangle subBorders, ref Vector2 spawnPoint, float amount)
3546 {
3547 float maxMovement = 5000;
3548 float totalAmount = 0;
3549 bool foundBottom = TryRaycastToBottom(subBorders, ref spawnPoint);
3550 while (!IsSideBlocked(subBorders, amount > 0))
3551 {
3552 foundBottom = TryRaycastToBottom(subBorders, ref spawnPoint);
3553 totalAmount += amount;
3554 spawnPoint = new Vector2(spawnPoint.X + amount, spawnPoint.Y);
3555 if (Math.Abs(totalAmount) > maxMovement)
3556 {
3557 Debug.WriteLine($"Moving the sub {subName} failed.");
3558 break;
3559 }
3560 }
3561 return foundBottom;
3562 }
3563 }

3566 {

3570 var wp = waypoints.GetRandom(Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
