3581 bool TryRaycastToBottom(Rectangle subBorders, ref Vector2 spawnPoint)
3582 {
3583 // Shoot five rays and pick the highest hit point.
3584 int rayCount = 5;
3585 var positions = new Vector2[rayCount];
3586 bool hit = false;
3587 for (int i = 0; i < rayCount; i++)
3588 {
3589 float quarterWidth = subBorders.Width * 0.25f;
3590 Vector2 rayStart = spawnPoint;
3591 switch (i)
3592 {
3593 case 1:
3594 rayStart = new Vector2(spawnPoint.X - quarterWidth, spawnPoint.Y);
3595 break;
3596 case 2:
3597 rayStart = new Vector2(spawnPoint.X + quarterWidth, spawnPoint.Y);
3598 break;
3599 case 3:
3600 rayStart = new Vector2(spawnPoint.X - quarterWidth / 2, spawnPoint.Y);
3601 break;
3602 case 4:
3603 rayStart = new Vector2(spawnPoint.X + quarterWidth / 2, spawnPoint.Y);
3604 break;
3605 }
3606 var simPos = ConvertUnits.ToSimUnits(rayStart);
3607 var body = Submarine.PickBody(simPos, new Vector2(simPos.X, -1),
3608 customPredicate: f => f.Body?.UserData is VoronoiCell cell && cell.Body.BodyType == BodyType.Static && !ExtraWalls.Any(w => w.Body == f.Body),
3609 collisionCategory: Physics.CollisionLevel | Physics.CollisionWall);
3610 if (body != null)
3611 {
3612 positions[i] = ConvertUnits.ToDisplayUnits(Submarine.LastPickedPosition) + new Vector2(0, subBorders.Height / 2);
3613 hit = true;
3614 }
3615 }
3616 float highestPoint = positions.Max(p => p.Y);
3617 spawnPoint = new Vector2(spawnPoint.X, highestPoint);
3618 return hit;
3619 }
3620
3621 bool IsSideBlocked(Rectangle subBorders, bool front)
3622 {
3623 // Shoot three rays and check whether any of them hits.
3624 int rayCount = 3;
3625 Vector2 halfSize = subBorders.Size.ToVector2() / 2;
3626 Vector2 quarterSize = halfSize / 2;
3627 var positions = new Vector2[rayCount];
3628 for (int i = 0; i < rayCount; i++)
3629 {
3630 float dir = front ? 1 : -1;
3631 Vector2 rayStart;
3632 Vector2 to;
3633 switch (i)
3634 {
3635 case 1:
3636 rayStart = new Vector2(spawnPoint.X + halfSize.X * dir, spawnPoint.Y + quarterSize.Y);
3637 to = new Vector2(spawnPoint.X + (halfSize.X - quarterSize.X) * dir, rayStart.Y);
3638 break;
3639 case 2:
3640 rayStart = new Vector2(spawnPoint.X + halfSize.X * dir, spawnPoint.Y - quarterSize.Y);
3641 to = new Vector2(spawnPoint.X + (halfSize.X - quarterSize.X) * dir, rayStart.Y);
3642 break;
3643 case 0:
3644 default:
3645 rayStart = spawnPoint;
3646 to = new Vector2(spawnPoint.X + halfSize.X * dir, rayStart.Y);
3647 break;
3648 }
3649 Vector2 simPos = ConvertUnits.ToSimUnits(rayStart);
3650 if (Submarine.PickBody(simPos, ConvertUnits.ToSimUnits(to),
3651 customPredicate: f => f.Body?.UserData is VoronoiCell cell,
3652 collisionCategory: Physics.CollisionLevel | Physics.CollisionWall) != null)
3653 {
3654 return true;
3655 }
3656 }
3657 return false;
3658 }

3660 bool IsBlocked(Vector2 pos, Point size, float maxDistanceMultiplier = 1)
3661 {
3662 float maxDistance = size.Multiply(maxDistanceMultiplier).ToVector2().LengthSquared();
3663 Rectangle bounds = ToolBox.GetWorldBounds(pos.ToPoint(), size);
3664 if (Ruins.Any(r => ToolBox.GetWorldBounds(r.Area.Center, r.Area.Size).IntersectsWorld(bounds)))
3665 {
3666 return true;
3667 }
3668 if (Caves.Any(c =>
3669 ToolBox.GetWorldBounds(c.Area.Center, c.Area.Size).IntersectsWorld(bounds) ||
3670 ToolBox.GetWorldBounds(c.StartPos, new Point(1500)).IntersectsWorld(bounds)))
3671 {
3672 return true;
3673 }
3674 return cells.Any(c => c.Body != null && Vector2.DistanceSquared(pos, c.Center) <= maxDistance && c.BodyVertices.Any(v => bounds.ContainsWorld(v)));
3675 }

3681 private void CreateWrecks()
3682 {
3683 var totalSW = new Stopwatch();
3684 totalSW.Start();
3685 var wreckFiles = ContentPackageManager.EnabledPackages.All
3686 .SelectMany(p => p.GetFiles<WreckFile>())
3687 .OrderBy(f => f.UintIdentifier).ToList();
3688 if (wreckFiles.None())
3689 {
3690 DebugConsole.ThrowError("No wreck files found in the selected content packages!");
3691 return;
3692 }
3693 wreckFiles.Shuffle(Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
3694
3695 int minWreckCount = Math.Min(Loaded.GenerationParams.MinWreckCount, wreckFiles.Count);
3696 int maxWreckCount = Math.Min(Loaded.GenerationParams.MaxWreckCount, wreckFiles.Count);
3697 int wreckCount = Rand.Range(minWreckCount, maxWreckCount + 1, Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
3698
3699 if (GameMain.GameSession?.GameMode?.Missions.Any(m => m.Prefab.RequireWreck) ?? false)
3700 {
3701 wreckCount = Math.Max(wreckCount, 1);
3702 }
3703
3704 Wrecks = new List<Submarine>(wreckCount);
3705 for (int i = 0; i < wreckCount; i++)
3706 {
3707 //how many times we'll try placing another sub before giving up
3708 const int MaxSubsToTry = 2;
3709 int attempts = 0;
3710 while (wreckFiles.Any() && attempts < MaxSubsToTry)

4106 public void SpawnCorpses()
4107 {
4108 if (GameMain.NetworkMember != null && GameMain.NetworkMember.IsClient) { return; }
4109
4110 foreach (Submarine wreck in Wrecks)
4111 {
4112 int corpseCount = Rand.Range(Loaded.GenerationParams.MinCorpseCount, Loaded.GenerationParams.MaxCorpseCount + 1);
4113 var allSpawnPoints = WayPoint.WayPointList.FindAll(wp => wp.Submarine == wreck && wp.CurrentHull != null);
4114 var pathPoints = allSpawnPoints.FindAll(wp => wp.SpawnType == SpawnType.Path);
4115 pathPoints.Shuffle(Rand.RandSync.Unsynced);
4116 var corpsePoints = allSpawnPoints.FindAll(wp => wp.SpawnType == SpawnType.Corpse);
4117 corpsePoints.Shuffle(Rand.RandSync.Unsynced);
4118
4119 if (!corpsePoints.Any() && !pathPoints.Any()) { continue; }
4120
4121 int spawnCounter = 0;
4122 for (int j = 0; j < corpseCount; j++)
4123 {
4124 WayPoint sp = corpsePoints.FirstOrDefault() ?? pathPoints.FirstOrDefault();
4125 JobPrefab job = sp?.AssignedJob;
4126 CorpsePrefab selectedPrefab;
4127 if (job == null)
4128 {
4129 selectedPrefab = GetCorpsePrefab(p => p.SpawnPosition == PositionType.Wreck);
4130 }
4131 else
4132 {
4133 selectedPrefab = GetCorpsePrefab(p => p.SpawnPosition == PositionType.Wreck && (p.Job == "any" || p.Job == job.Identifier));
4134 if (selectedPrefab == null)
4135 {
4136 corpsePoints.Remove(sp);
4137 pathPoints.Remove(sp);
4138 sp = corpsePoints.FirstOrDefault(sp => sp.AssignedJob == null) ?? pathPoints.FirstOrDefault(sp => sp.AssignedJob == null);
4139 // Deduce the job from the selected prefab
4140 selectedPrefab = GetCorpsePrefab(p => p.SpawnPosition == PositionType.Wreck);
4141 }
4142 }
4143 if (selectedPrefab == null) { continue; }
4144 Vector2 worldPos;
4145 if (sp == null)
4146 {
4147 if (!TryGetExtraSpawnPoint(out worldPos))
4148 {
4149 break;
4150 }
4151 }
4152 else
4153 {
4154 worldPos = sp.WorldPosition;
4155 corpsePoints.Remove(sp);
4156 pathPoints.Remove(sp);
4157 }
4158
4159 job ??= selectedPrefab.GetJobPrefab();
4160 if (job == null) { continue; }
4161
4162 var characterInfo = new CharacterInfo(CharacterPrefab.HumanSpeciesName, jobOrJobPrefab: job, randSync: Rand.RandSync.ServerAndClient);
4163 var corpse = Character.Create(CharacterPrefab.HumanSpeciesName, worldPos, ToolBox.RandomSeed(8), characterInfo, hasAi: true, createNetworkEvent: true);
4164 corpse.AnimController.FindHull(worldPos, setSubmarine: true);
4165 corpse.TeamID = CharacterTeamType.None;
4166 corpse.EnableDespawn = false;
4167 selectedPrefab.GiveItems(corpse, wreck);
4168 corpse.Kill(CauseOfDeathType.Unknown, causeOfDeathAffliction: null, log: false);
4169 corpse.GiveIdCardTags(sp);
4170#if SERVER
4171 if (selectedPrefab.MinMoney >= 0 && selectedPrefab.MaxMoney > 0)
4172 {
4173 corpse.Wallet.Give(Rand.Range(selectedPrefab.MinMoney, selectedPrefab.MaxMoney, Rand.RandSync.Unsynced));
4174 }
4175#endif
4176 spawnCounter++;

4181 return ToolBox.SelectWeightedRandom(filteredPrefabs.ToList(), filteredPrefabs.Select(p => p.Commonness).ToList(), Rand.RandSync.Unsynced);
4182 }
4183 }
4184#if DEBUG
4185 DebugConsole.NewMessage($"{spawnCounter}/{corpseCount} corpses spawned in {wreck.Info.Name}.", spawnCounter == corpseCount ? Color.Green : Color.Yellow);
4186#endif

4188 {
4189 point = Vector2.Zero;
